t%20Garden%20Glamping%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20lockdown%20DIY%20project%20went%20viral%20on%20the%20internet%20after%20it%20was%20picked%20up%20by%20an%20online%20publication.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20started%20messaging%20me%20through%20social%20media%20asking%20if%20they%20could%20book%20it%20for%20a%20holiday%2C%20which%20at%20the%20time%20seemed%20crazy%20to%20me.%20I%20thought%2C%20'Why%20would%20you%20want%20to%20come%20and%20book%20something%20that%20I've%20built%20in%20the%20garden%3F'%26quot%3B%20Green%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EBut%20with%20nothing%20to%20lose%2C%20Green%20decided%20to%20take%20the%20plunge%20%E2%80%94%20and%20listed%20his%20glamping%20pod%20on%20Airbnb.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWithin%20days%2C%20it%20was%20fully%20booked%20for%20months%20in%20advance.%20The%20response%20was%20just%20unbelievable%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20then%20realized%2C%20obviously%2C%20there%20was%20a%20gap%20in%20the%20market%20for%20what%20I'd%20made%20and%20decided%20to%20then%20pursue%20it%20as%20a%20career.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222146%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20exterior%20of%20the%20first%20glamping%20pod%20that%20Green%20and%20his%20family%20built.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64b77c371ccd1e00198abfd3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221609%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20exterior%20of%20the%20first%20glamping%20pod%20that%20Green%20and%20his%20family%20built.%3Cp%3EThe%20Secret%20Garden%20Glamping%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20first%20pod%20was%20officially%20opened%20to%20guests%20in%20June%202020%2C%20Green%20applied%20for%20planning%20permission%20to%20build%20a%20proper%20glamping%20site%20on%20the%20four%20acres%20of%20woodland%20that%20he%20owned%20beside%20his%20house.%20He%20was%20granted%20permission%20about%20nine%20months%20later%2C%20in%20March%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20then%2C%20Green's%20collection%20of%20glamping%20pods%20has%20grown%20to%20nine%20units%20%E2%80%94%20and%20he's%20still%20building%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20building%20another%20four.%20Two%20of%20them%20open%20around%20August%2C%20and%20then%20we've%20got%20two%20more%20opening%20later%20in%20the%20year%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EEach%20glamping%20pod%20takes%20about%20three%20months%20to%20build.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20progress%20photo%20of%20the%20glamping%20pod%20construction%20process.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64b78e301ccd1e00198ac456%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EProgress%20photo%20of%20the%20glamping%20pod%20construction%20process.%3Cp%3EThe%20Secret%20Garden%20Glamping%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20Green%20can%20build%20the%20pods%20quicker%20now%20since%20he%20can%20hire%20help%2C%20he%20prefers%20to%20take%20his%20time%20with%20the%20projects.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20now%2C%20I%20don't%20have%20a%20set%20of%20plans%20when%20I%20start%2C%26quot%3B%20Green%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20never%20know%20what%20I'm%20building%20when%20I%20start%20off%2C%20it%20evolves%20as%20we%20go%20along%2C%20so%20having%20that%20time%20to%20sit%20back%20each%20day%20and%20work%20out%20what's%20missing%20or%20what%20we%20need%20to%20add%20makes%20a%20whole%20world%20of%20difference.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20design%20of%20the%20glamping%20pods%20is%20inspired%20by%20the%20setting%20of%20the%20popular%20reality%20dating%20show%2C%20%26quot%3BLove%20Island.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22One%20of%20Green's%20glamping%20pods.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64be2835bea34400195f96b0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOne%20of%20Green's%20glamping%20pods.%3Cp%3EThe%20Secret%20Garden%20Glamping%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20show%2C%20singles%20are%20brought%20to%20a%20private%20island%20villa.%20They%20are%20given%20a%20series%20of%20tasks%20to%20complete%20with%20a%20partner%20and%20keep%20swapping%20until%20they%20fall%20in%20love.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20the%20%26quot%3BLove%20Island%26quot%3B%20villa%2C%20Green's%20glamping%20pods%20have%20spacious%20outdoor%20decks%2C%20hot%20tubs%2C%20and%20lots%20of%20fairy%20lights.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20we%20started%20building%20it%2C%20we%20quickly%20realized%20there%20was%20no%20way%20we%20were%20going%20on%20a%20summer%20holiday%20in%202020%2C%26quot%3B%20Green%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%2C%20watching%20'Love%20Island'%20and%20seeing%20the%20villa%2C%20I%20was%20trying%20to%20recreate%20something%20that%20felt%20like%20we%20were%20on%20holiday%20abroad.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EGreen%20says%20that%2C%20on%20average%2C%20it%20costs%20him%20around%20%C2%A340%2C000%20to%20%C2%A350%2C000%2C%20or%20%2451%2C000%20to%20%2464%2C000%2C%20to%20build%20each%20of%20the%20new%20glamping%20pods.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223023%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20view%20of%20the%20first%20floor%20from%20the%20loft%20of%20one%20of%20the%20glamping%20pods.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64be3579ed4f460019619b77%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20view%20of%20the%20first%20floor%20from%20the%20loft%20of%20one%20of%20the%20glamping%20pods.%3Cp%3EThe%20Secret%20Garden%20Glamping%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20contrast%2C%20he%20had%20only%20spent%20about%20%C2%A36%2C000%2C%20or%20%247%2C700%2C%20building%20the%20first%20glamping%20pod%20with%20his%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEach%20one's%20getting%20bigger%20and%20more%20elaborate%2C%20with%20more%20things%20in%20it%2C%20than%20the%20one%20before%2C%26quot%3B%20Green%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20then%20obviously%2C%20since%20COVID-19%2C%20the%20price%20of%20everything%20has%20skyrocketed%20compared%20to%20what%20it%20was%20back%20then.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20expensive%20project%20is%20a%20treehouse%20named%20%26quot%3BThe%20Tree%20Tops%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20it%20cost%20nearly%20%C2%A3100%2C000%2C%20or%20%24128%2C500%2C%20to%20build%2C%20he%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BThat%20was%20the%20biggest%20project%20we%20had.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWhile%20the%20first%20glamping%20pod%20consists%20mostly%20of%20items%20that%20Green%20found%20on%20Facebook%20Marketplace%20or%20eBay%2C%20the%20furniture%20in%20the%20other%20units%20is%20custom-made.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22One%20of%20the%20bedrooms%20in%20the%20glamping%20pods.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64b78f0a1ccd1e00198ac500%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222274%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOne%20of%20the%20bedrooms%20in%20the%20glamping%20pods.%3Cp%3EThe%20Secret%20Garden%20Glamping%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20we've%20found%20is%20that%20with%20small%20spaces%20%E2%80%94%20all%20the%20units%2C%20in%20theory%2C%20are%20kind%20of%20like%20tiny%20homes%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20very%20hard%20to%20buy%20off-the-shelf%20furniture%20or%20fittings%20that%20work%2C%26quot%3B%20Green%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20now%20we%20build%20most%20of%20the%20stuff%20on-site%20to%20maximize%20the%20use%20of%20space%20in%20each%20unit.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20now%20heads%20a%20team%20of%2014%20people%20to%20help%20him%20run%20the%20business%2C%20which%20is%20called%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thesecretgardenglamping.uk%2F%5C%22%3EThe%20Secret%20Garden%20Glamping%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUp%20until%20the%20last%20two%2C%20it%20was%20all%20just%20me%20on%20my%20own%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20things%20have%20scaled%20up%20with%20the%20business%20now%2C%20not%20just%20on%20the%20building%20side%20of%20things%2C%20but%20also%20in%20running%20the%20site%2C%20managing%20social%20media%2C%20and%20managing%20customer%20relations.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EGreen's%20two%20children%20still%20give%20inputs%20on%20the%20newer%20builds.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20son%20is%20just%20like%20me%2C%20he%20wants%20to%20be%20building%20stuff%20with%20me.%20So%20I%20teach%20him%20different%20things%20he%20can%20do%20on%20a%20daily%20basis%2C%26quot%3B%20Green%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Derry's%20son%20helped%20out%20with%20construction%20wherever%20he%20could.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64b78df81ccd1e00198ac424%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDerry's%20children%20helped%20out%20with%20construction%20of%20their%20first%20pod.%3Cp%3EThe%20Secret%20Garden%20Glamping%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20then%20my%20daughter%2C%20she%20just%20loves%20spending%20time%20in%20them.%20Throughout%20the%20construction%20process%2C%20we%20kind%20of%20stay%20in%20it%2C%20and%20I%20see%20what%20she%20thinks%20is%20missing%20or%20anything%20that%20she'd%20like%20in%20there.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223023%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Green's%20daughter%20stands%20in%20the%20glass%20doorway%20of%20one%20of%20the%20glamping%20pods%20on%20their%20property.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64bf6eadbea344001960a62b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGreen's%20daughter%20stands%20in%20the%20glass%20doorway%20of%20one%20of%20the%20glamping%20pods%20on%20their%20property.%3Cp%3EThe%20Secret%20Garden%20Glamping%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20glamping%20pods%20can%20be%20booked%20on%20Green's%20website%2C%20and%20they%20range%20between%20%C2%A3195%20to%20%C2%A3285%20per%20night.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Insider%20checked%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thesecretgardenglamping.uk%2Fbook-now%5C%22%3Ethe%20site%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20all%20the%20glamping%20pods%20were%20fully%20booked%20up%20until%20November%20%E2%80%94%20but%20even%20then%2C%20there's%20only%20one%20glamping%20pod%20left%20for%20a%20three-night%20stay%20for%20the%20month.%20There%20are%20also%20barely%20any%20availabilities%20in%20December.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20cheapest%20glamping%20pod%20is%20the%20first%20pod%20that%20Green%20ever%20built%2C%20and%20it's%20a%20yurt%20called%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thesecretgardenglamping.uk%2Fthe-retreat%5C%22%3EThe%20Retreat%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20per%20The%20Secret%20Garden%20Glamping%20site.%20It%20sleeps%20four%20guests%20and%20comes%20with%20a%20hot%20tub%20and%20a%20sauna.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20priciest%20glamping%20pod%20to%20stay%20in%20is%20the%20aforementioned%20treehouse%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thesecretgardenglamping.uk%2Fthe-tree-tops%5C%22%3EThe%20Tree%20Tops%3C%2Fa%3E.%26quot%3B%20It's%20the%20first%20glamping%20pod%20on%20the%20property%20to%20sleep%20six%20guests.%20Apart%20from%20a%20hot%20tub%2C%20it%20also%20comes%20with%20a%20slide%20and%20a%20pool%20table.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20bathroom%20with%20glass%20doors%20in%20one%20of%20the%20glamping%20pods.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64b78ed776558a00189d423a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222274%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20bathroom%20in%20one%20of%20the%20glamping%20pods.%3Cp%3EThe%20Secret%20Garden%20Glamping%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20kind%20of%20a%20standard%20list%20now.%20So%20they've%20all%20got%20hot%20tubs%2C%20they've%20all%20got%20bar%20areas%2C%20they've%20all%20got%20outdoor%20seating%20areas%2C%26quot%3B%20Green%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20all%20the%20glamping%20pods%20are%20based%20around%20the%20same%20%26quot%3BLove%20Island%26quot%3B%20theme%2C%20each%20one%20has%20something%20that%20the%20other%20one%20doesn't%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20example%2C%20one%20that%20we%20just%20opened%20that's%20called%20'The%20Oasis'%20has%20a%20huge%20outdoor%20cinema%20while%20'The%20Tree%20Tops'%20has%20got%20an%20outdoor%20pool%20table%2C%26quot%3B%20Green%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EDespite%20the%20%26quot%3BLove%20Island%26quot%3B%20theme%2C%20Green%20says%20that%20most%20of%20his%20guests%20are%20women.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20room%20inside%20one%20of%20the%20glamping%20pods.%20It's%20spacious%20and%20comes%20with%20a%20television%20as%20well%20as%20two%20beds.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64b78e921ccd1e00198ac4a3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERooms%20in%20the%20glamping%20pods%20are%20luxurious.%20This%20particular%20room%20is%20extremely%20spacious%20and%20comes%20with%20two%20beds%20as%20well%20as%20a%20television.%3Cp%3EThe%20Secret%20Garden%20Glamping%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20couples%20and%20families%20with%20young%20children%20do%20come%20to%20stay%20at%20his%20glamping%20pods%2C%20about%20half%20of%20Green's%20guests%20are%20groups%20of%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey're%20anywhere%20between%20the%20ages%20of%2020%20and%2060%2C%20they%20want%20to%20get%20away%20from%20the%20husbands%20or%20the%20kids%20or%20things%20like%20that.%20And%20they%20just%20come%20in%20with%20their%20friends%20to%20reconnect%20and%20relax%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EEach%20glamping%20pod%20unit%20is%20completely%20enclosed%20and%20separate%20from%20the%20rest%20to%20ensure%20his%20guests'%20privacy.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20outdoor%20bar%20and%20hot%20tub%20in%20one%20of%20the%20glamping%20pods.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64b63a81db9026001935621a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAn%20outdoor%20bar%20and%20hot%20tub%20in%20one%20of%20the%20glamping%20pods.%3Cp%3EThe%20Secret%20Garden%20Glamping%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EEach%20of%20the%20units%20is%20set%20in%20a%20different%20part%20of%20the%20woodland%2C%20Green%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20kind%20of%20what%20really%20made%20the%20first%20go%20so%20viral.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20especially%20during%20COVID-19%2C%20people%20were%20looking%20for%20unique%20accommodations%20with%20dedicated%20facilities%2C%20and%20they%20wanted%20to%20be%20away%20from%20everybody%20else%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ESetting%20up%20the%20necessary%20electrical%20and%20water%20infrastructure%20was%20one%20of%20the%20most%20complex%20parts%20of%20building%20the%20glamping%20pods.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20outdoor%20cinema%20in%20one%20of%20the%20glamping%20pods.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64b63a76db90260019356216%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAn%20outdoor%20cinema%20in%20one%20of%20the%20glamping%20pods.%3Cp%3EThe%20Secret%20Garden%20Glamping%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20when%20I%20did%20the%20first%20one%2C%20it%20was%20pretty%20simple%20because%20it%20was%20near%20the%20house%2C%20so%20it%20was%20connected%20to%20the%20power%20supply%20and%20the%20water%20from%20the%20house%2C%26quot%3B%20Green%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20subsequent%20glamping%20pods%20are%20located%20in%20the%20woodlands%2C%20which%20are%20about%200.3%20miles%20away%20from%20the%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGetting%20infrastructure%20down%20here%20was%20the%20first%20task%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20we've%20got%20full%20mains%2C%20water%2C%20waste%2C%20and%20power%20down%20here.%20We%20actually%20generate%20our%20own%20power%20now%2C%20which%20then%20provides%20for%20the%20entire%20glamping%20site.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20%26quot%3BLove%20Island%26quot%3B-inspired%20glamping%20pods%20each%20have%20a%20mix%20of%20indoor%20and%20outdoor%20spaces.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64be3550bea34400195f9f9f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20indoor%20and%20outdoor%20spaces%20of%20the%20glamping%20pods%20blend%20seamlessly%20with%20one%20another.%3Cp%3EThe%20Secret%20Garden%20Glamping%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20though%20the%20first%20glamping%20pod%20was%20right%20beside%20Green's%20home%2C%20a%20new%20wall%20has%20been%20built%20to%20separate%20the%20spaces.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20house%20is%20now%20entirely%20separate%20from%20the%20glamping%20site.%20It's%20got%20its%20own%20entrance%2C%20its%20own%20main%20car%20park%2C%20and%20then%20from%20there%2C%20it%20all%20comes%20down%20into%20the%20woods%2C%26quot%3B%20Green%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20even%20that%20first%20unit%20that%20we%20did%20is%20totally%20enclosed%20on%20its%20own%20in%20that%20part%20of%20the%20site%20now.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EGreen%20says%20that%20building%20the%20glamping%20pods%20was%20the%20easiest%20part%20of%20running%20the%20business.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20exterior%20porch%20of%20one%20of%20the%20glamping%20pods.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64b78cad76558a00189d4132%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGreen's%20glamping%20pods%20are%20luxurious%2C%20and%20they%20come%20with%20amenities%20such%20as%20outdoor%20decks%2C%20hot%20tubs%2C%20and%20campfires.%3Cp%3EThe%20Secret%20Garden%20Glamping%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBuilding%20the%20units%20is%20what%20I%20love%20to%20do.%20It's%20a%20hundred%20percent%20not%20a%20job.%20It's%20just%20fun%20for%20me%20%E2%80%94%20that's%20my%20hobby%20and%20I%20love%20doing%20it%2C%20but%20actually%20trying%20to%20turn%20that%20into%20a%20business%20was%20tough%2C%26quot%3B%20Green%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EComing%20from%20a%20job%20that%20was%20less%20customer-facing%2C%20he%20added%20that%20managing%20the%20glamping%20business%20came%20with%20a%20whole%20new%20set%20of%20challenges%2C%20such%20as%20figuring%20out%20what%20guests%20need%20and%20how%20to%20manage%20his%20staff.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EFor%20those%20who%20want%20to%20take%20on%20a%20DIY%20project%2C%20Green%20has%20one%20piece%20of%20advice%3A%20Stop%20worrying%2C%20and%20just%20give%20it%20a%20go.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20outdoor%20deck%20of%20one%20of%20the%20glamping%20pods%2C%20which%20has%20a%20mini%20bonfire.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64b790a876558a00189d434c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESome%20of%20the%20glamping%20pods%20have%20an%20outdoor%20deck%20with%20a%20bonfire.%3Cp%3EThe%20Secret%20Garden%20Glamping%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Csection%20data-slideshow-type%3D%5C%22one-page-view%5C%22%20data-track-content%20data-track-page-area%3D%5C%22Post%5C%22%20data-post-type%3D%5C%22slideshow%5C%22%20data-slideshow-container%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%3Csection%20data-slideshow-inner-content%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20Green%20started%20this%20project%2C%20the%20most%20he%20had%20done%20in%20terms%20of%20DIY%20was%20painting%20and%20putting%20new%20wallpaper%20up%20in%20the%20living%20room.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20have%20a%20building%20background%20either%2C%20but%20what%20I%20found%20is%20that%20if%20you%20give%20it%20a%20go%2C%20you