ovation%2C%20while%20other%20marketers%20are%20still%20on%20the%20sidelines%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Examples%20of%20Dispatch's%20sales%20asset%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64c26599101bd0001929d15a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDispatch%20provides%20a%20way%20for%20users%20to%20make%20purchases%20in%20games%20and%20websites%20without%20navigating%20to%20another%20site.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Dispatch%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EMany%20CMOs%20are%20not%20prioritizing%20Web3%20right%20now%20thanks%20to%20the%20crypto%20crisis%20hangover%2C%20and%20inflation.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EHowever%2C%20some%20activewear%20and%20luxury%20brands%20are%20leveraging%20NFTs%20and%20the%20metaverse%20in%20ways%20other%20marketers%20can%20learn%20from.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EDispatch%2C%20which%20provides%20a%20Web3%20solution%2C%20is%20trying%20to%20help%20CMOs%20get%20beyond%20the%20hype%20and%20add%20new%20tools%20to%20their%20repertoire.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fcrypto-crash%5C%22%3Ecrypto%20crash%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20began%20in%202022%20decimated%20more%20than%20just%20the%20real-world%20wallets%20of%20investors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20crisis%20sapped%20the%20forward%20momentum%20of%20the%20emerging%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fwhat-is-web3%5C%22%3EWeb3%20marketing%20landscape%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20where%20business%20leaders%20were%20eager%20to%20figure%20out%20how%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finvest-nft-investor-bored-ape-yacht-club-art-market-ceo-2022-4%5C%22%3EBored%20Ape%20NFTs%3C%2Fa%3E%20could%20translate%20to%20new%20channels%20to%20reach%20consumers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUse%20cases%20for%20Web3%20are%20still%20evolving%20but%20it%20all%20centers%20around%20the%20same%20principles%20that%20spawned%20crypto%20%E2%80%94%20decentralized%20applications%20underpinned%20by%20blockchain%20technology.%20It%20allows%20people%20to%20own%20their%20data%20and%20digital%20assets%2C%20and%20so%20opens%20up%20possibilities%20for%20distributing%20purchase%20options%20in%20new%20and%20surprising%20places%20across%20the%20internet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EByron%20Sorrells%2C%20CEO%20and%20cofounder%20of%20Dispatch%2C%20which%20provides%20friction-free%20purchasing%20in%20places%20like%20game%20experiences%2C%20says%20the%20reset%20was%20not%20necessarily%20a%20bad%20thing.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20now%20seeing%20the%20distinction%20between%20speculation%2C%20financial%20engineering%2C%20FOMO%2C%20'let's%20drop%20some%20pictures%20of%20rabbits%20and%20see%20if%20the%20price%20goes%20up'%2C%20and%20the%20real%20utility%20behind%20the%20technology%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Sorrells.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20shame%20it%20took%20these%20big%20events%20for%20that%20to%20happen%2C%20but%20you%20do%20start%20to%20see%20that%20what's%20survived%20are%20some%20genuine%20use%20cases%2C%26quot%3B%20Sorrells%20said.%20%26quot%3BWeb3%20is%20not%20just%20some%20big%20wholesale%20replacement%20for%20what%20we%20used%20to%20do.%20It's%20just%20new%20technology%20that%20can%20augment%20the%20things%20we've%20always%20done.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20as%20the%20potential%20applications%20seem%20tantalizingly%20possibly%2C%20CMOs%20can%20be%20overwhelmed%20by%20the%20array%20of%20technology%20available%20to%20them.%20%26quot%3BWe're%20oversaturated%20with%20technology%20solutions%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Marija%20Zivanovic-Smith%2C%20chief%20marketing%20officer%20at%20IEX%20Group%2C%20parent%20company%20of%20Dispatch.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENew%20tech%20for%20tech's%20sake%20is%20out%20of%20fashion%3B%20Web3%20providers%20need%20to%20speak%20to%20the%20business%20problems%20that%20CMOs%20and%20their%20brands%20are%20facing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20curiosity%20that%20we%20have%20is%20not%20driven%20by%20Web3%20or%20blockchain%20or%20the%20tech%20itself%2C%26quot%3B%20Zivanovic-Smith%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20solving%20for%20increasing%20digital%20loyalty%2C%20solving%20for%20the%20problems%20that%20we're%20facing%20with%20losing%2030%25%20accuracy%20on%20targeting%20algorithms%20when%20Apple%20did%20away%20with%20cookies.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWeb3%20adoption%20is%20picking%20up%20slowly%20for%20both%20buyers%20and%20sellers%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWeb3%20adoption%20is%20growing%20again%2C%20says%20Matt%20Moorut%2C%20director%2C%20analyst%20at%20Gartner%2C%20but%20not%20at%20the%20same%20pace%20as%2012%20to%2018%20months%20ago%20when%20metaverse%20hype%20was%20at%20its%20peak.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERecovery%20has%20been%20complicated%20by%20ongoing%20crypto%20volatility%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20onset%20of%20inflation%2C%20which%20has%20caused%20marketers%20to%20avoid%20investing%20in%20risky%2C%20untested%20channels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20to%20say%20Web3%20is%20dead%2C%26quot%3B%20Moorut%20said.%20Marketers%20are%20still%20interested%2C%20%26quot%3Bbut%20rather%20than%20rushing%20forwards%20with%20it%2C%20they're%20being%20more%20sensible%20and%20trying%20to%20unpick%20those%20use%20cases%20where%20Web3%20technologies%20are%20still%20valuable%20for%20the%20organization.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMoorut%20says%20that%20activewear%20and%20some%20luxury%20brands%20are%20among%20the%20most%20advanced%20with%20Web3.%20%26quot%3BNike%20and%20Adidas%20in%20particular%20were%20two%20of%20the%20earliest%20ones%20to%20build%20blockchain%20technologies%20into%20loyalty%20programs%20and%20build%20communities%20around%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22458%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Nike%20poster%20showing%20a%20skeleton%20foot%20in%20a%20sneaker%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64c26fbf9440b70019271a9d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22686%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ENike%20released%20its%20first%20virtual%20collection%20in%20April%202023.%3Cp%3ENike%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20just%20about%20transactional%20NFT%20sales%2C%20but%20rather%20how%20Web3%20forms%20part%20of%20their%20customer%20experience%20strategy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENike%20rolled%20out%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.swoosh.nike%2F%5C%22%3E.Swoosh%20community%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20November%202022%2C%20with%20options%20for%20members%20to%20participate%20in%20activations%20online%20and%20in%20the%20real%20world%2C%20engage%20with%20Nike%20athletes%20and%20creatives%2C%20and%20use%20virtual%20Nike%20gear%20in%20games.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20April%202023%2C%20Nike%20launched%20its%20first%20virtual%20collection%2C%20called%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3Daf3eb77692bd63f2d3cc4c343d078e5bd3a320dcee7e07f23030157cc5b6ae57%26postID%3D64be7f8875976ff3ff4c0bf6%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.nike.com%252Flaunch%252Ft%252Fdot-swoosh-our-force-1-collection%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOur%20Force%201%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20which%20was%20co-created%20by%20its%20community.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBig%20brand%20moments%20like%20this%20aside%2C%20consumer%20engagement%20with%20Web3%20activations%20is%20still%20on%20the%20low%20side%2C%20and%20it%20skews%20towards%20the%20young%2C%20affluent%2C%20male%20demographic.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20number%20of%20consumers%20out%20there%20that%20have%20used%20an%20NFT%20or%20have%20a%20crypto%20wallet%20is%20really%20low%20if%20you%20look%20at%20the%20total%20population%2C%26quot%3B%20Moorut%20says.%20%26quot%3BUntil%20there's%20a%20big%20sea%20change%20in%20the%20consumer%20adoption%2C%20it's%20going%20to%20be%20kind%20of%20an%20edge%20case%20for%20a%20marketer%2C%20versus%20the%20core%20of%20most%20re