olls.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EA%20USC%20political%20science%20professor%20told%20Insider%20that%20DeSantis%20hasn't%20hit%20Trump%20%26quot%3Bhard%20enough.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ERon%20DeSantis%20has%20privately%20hoped%20that%20former%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20mountain%20of%20legal%20troubles%20would%20slow%20his%20opponent%20down%2C%20but%20polls%20continue%20to%20show%20the%20Florida%20governor%20trailing%20behind%20in%20second%20place%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2023%2F07%2F23%2Fus%2Fpolitics%2Fdesantis-campaign-reboot.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20New%20York%20Times%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20eight%20months%20until%20the%20primaries%2C%20the%20public's%20opinion%20can%20still%20change%20%E2%80%94%20and%20so%20can%20Trump's%20legal%20standing.%20But%20so%20far%20the%20GOP%20base%20has%20primarily%20stood%20behind%20the%20former%20president%20despite%20his%20avalanche%20of%20legal%20woes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20indictments%20haven't%20impacted%20Trump%20as%20much%20as%20his%20opponents%20had%20hoped%20because%20he%20relies%20on%20an%20old%20playbook%20that%20has%20so%20far%20worked%20for%20his%20supporters%3A%20Deny%2C%20deflect%2C%20and%20blame%20the%20Democrats.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20witch%20hunt%20is%20all%20about%20election%20interference%20and%20a%20complete%20and%20total%20political%20weaponization%20of%20law%20enforcement%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20wrote%2C%20in%20all%20capitals%2C%20on%20Truth%20Social%2C%20after%20special%20counsel%20Jack%20Smith%20notified%20the%20former%20president%20that%20he%20is%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-jack-smith-wants-him-testify-to-jan6-grand-jury-2023-7%5C%22%3Etarget%20of%20the%20DOJ's%20January%206%20investigation%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20University%20of%20Southern%20California%20political%20science%20professor%20Christian%20Grose%2C%20if%20Trump%20was%20to%20apologize%20and%20try%20to%20move%20past%20the%20issue%2C%20it%20could%20have%20hurt%20him%20more.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20he's%20done%20(instead)%20is%20what%20he%20usually%20does%20as%20a%20strategy%20and%20just%20sort%20of%20denies%2C%20blames%20'left-wing'%20media%2C%20etc.%2C%26quot%3B%20Grose%20told%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BSo%20I%20think%20his%20strategy%20of%20blaming%20others%20for%20the%20legal%20woes%20that%20are%20upon%20him%20%E2%80%94%20that%20seems%20to%20help%20him%20rally%20the%20Republican%20base.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20Trump's%20top%20challenger%20for%20the%20GOP%20nomination%2C%20Grose%20said%20DeSantis%20hasn't%20quite%20%26quot%3Bhit%20him%20hard%20enough.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDeSantis%20tends%20to%20avoid%20saying%20what%20Trump%20has%20done%20is%20wrong%2C%26quot%3B%20Grose%20said.%20%26quot%3BHe%20has%20even%20gone%20on%20the%20record%20sometimes%20saying%20that%20these%20are%20unfair%20cases%20against%20the%20former%20president.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Trump%20was%20indicted%20a%20second%20time%20on%20charges%20related%20to%20mishandling%20classified%20documents%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdesantis-slams-doj-says-weaponizing-law-enforcement-against-trump-2023-6%5C%22%3EDeSantis%20came%20to%20Trump's%20side%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20following%20the%20former%20president's%20characterization%20that%20the%20Biden%20Administration%20had%20weaponized%20the%20Department%20of%20Justice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20it%20was%20clear%20Trump%20was%20also%20a%20target%20of%20the%20Justice%20Department's%20probe%20into%20the%20January%206%20riot%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnn.com%2F2023%2F07%2F18%2Fpolitics%2Fron-desantis-jake-tapper-interview-cnntv%2Findex.html%23%3A~%3Atext%3D%25E2%2580%259CI%2520do%2520not%2520wanna%2520see%2Cwith%2520a%2520mainstream%2520news%2520outlet.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDeSantis%20told%20CNN%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20hope%20he%20doesn't%20get%20charged.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENotable%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdesantis-slams-trump-fiscal-cultural-issues-left-gop-2024-campaign-2023-5%5C%22%3Eattacks%20on%20Trump%20from%20DeSantis%20or%20his%20campaign%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0have%20often%20been%20limited%20to%20hot-button%20culture%20war%20issues%20%E2%80%94%20in%20one%20recent%20ad%20attempting%20to%20paint%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdesantis-campaign-homophobic-transphobic-ad-backlash-2023-7%5C%22%3ETrump%20as%20someone%20sympathetic%20to%20LGBTQ%20groups%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20former%20president's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdesantis-slams-trump-fiscal-cultural-issues-left-gop-2024-campaign-2023-5%5C%22%3Ehandling%20of%20COVID-19%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20accusing%20him%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdesantis-campaign-appears-to-use-ai-images-trump-fauci-video-2023-6%5C%22%3Ekowtowing%20to%20Dr.%20Anthony%20Fauci%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAttacking%20Trump%20through%20his%20legal%20troubles%20is%20a%20delicate%20situation%2C%20Grose%20said.%20Voter%20opinion%20could%20change%20if%20any%20one%20of%20Trump's%20indictments%20leads%20to%20a%20conviction%2C%20but%20%26quot%3Bthere's%20a%20lot%20of%20in-between%20for%20that%20to%20happen.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20very%20tough%20line%20because%20so%20many%20of%20the%20voters%20DeSantis%20wants%20%E2%80%94%20they%20like%20Trump%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20professor%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20it's%20more%20about%3A%20Do%20you%20vote%20for%20somebody%20you%20find%20more%20electable%20even%20if%20you%20like%20Trump%20better%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EDeSantis%20is%20not%20a%20'memorable%20personality'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ECal%20Jillson%2C%20a%20political%20scientist%20at%20Southern%20Methodist%20University%2C%20echoed%20this%20sentiment%2C%20te