0all%20the%20things%20that%20make%20for%20a%20winning%20politician.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20hasn't%20caught%20on%20nationally%2C%20because%20he%20is%20a%20little%20awkward%2C%26quot%3B%20Jillson%20said.%20%26quot%3BHe%20is%20often%20expressionless%20and%20obviously%20doesn't%20enjoy%20retail%20campaigning%2C%20which%20is%20critical%20in%20places%20like%20Iowa%20and%20New%20Hampshire.%20So%20he%20doesn't%20have%20the%20whole%20toolkit%20that%20a%20politician%20like%20a%20Ronald%20Reagan%2C%20say%2C%20or%20a%20Bill%20Clinton%20or%20even%20a%20Donald%20Trump%20has.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20is%20not%2C%20fundamentally%2C%20a%20memorable%20personality%2C%26quot%3B%20Jillson%20continued%3A%20%26quot%3BAnd%20he%20doesn't%20have%20a%20second%20gear%2C%20apparently.%20He's%20not%20able%20to%20analyze%20his%20shortcomings%20and%20deal%20with%20them%20effectively%20and%20move%20from%20there.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-indictment-lawsuit-impact-polls-ron-desantis-2023-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690488920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F646e9a0363b4c50018c39a6c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-indictment-lawsuit-impact-polls-ron-desantis-2023-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Donald%20Trump's%20indictments%20and%20lawsuits%20haven't%20hurt%20his%20polling%20numbers%20because%20rival%20Republican%20Ron%20DeSantis%20won't%20say%20what%20Trump%20did%20is%20wrong.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22lloydlee%40insider.com%20(Lloyd%20Lee%2CHannah%20Getahun)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A35%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-indictment-lawsuit-impact-polls-ron-desantis-2023-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Allahabad%20HC%20judgment%20on%20Gyanvapi%20survey%20on%20August%203%