0teams%20have%20been%20formed%20for%20mass%20operation%20at%20several%20locations%20to%20arrest%20identified%20culprits%20and%20an%20Additional%20SP%20rank%20officer%20has%20been%20entrusted%20to%20investigate%20the%20case%2C%20under%20the%20constant%20supervision%20of%20other%20senior%20police%20officials%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20affidavit%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Centre%20underlined%20that%20the%20trial%20should%20be%20conducted%20in%20a%20time-bound%20manner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20approach%20of%20the%20Central%20Government%20is%20of%20zero%20tolerance%20towards%20any%20crimes%20against%20women.%20The%20Central%20Government%20considers%20the%20offences%20like%20the%20present%20one%20to%20be%20too%20heinous%20which%20deserve%20to%20be%20taken%20not%20only%20with%20the%20seriousness%20it%20deserves%20but%20justice%20should%20be%20seen%20to%20be%20done%20so%20that%20it%20has%20a%20deterrent%20effect%20throughout%20the%20nation%20with%20respect%20to%20crimes%20against%20women%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Centre%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20video%20from%20Manipur%2C%20coming%20ahead%20of%20the%20monsoon%20session%20of%20parliament%2C%20generated%20furore%20in%20the%20house%2C%20with%20the%20opposition%20demanding%20a%20statement%20from%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20government%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20none%20was%20coming%2C%20the%20opposition%20took%20a%20circuitous%20route%2C%20pushing%20for%20a%20no-confidence%20motion%20against%20the%20government%20which%20has%20been%20accepted%20by%20Speaker%20Om%20Birla.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOpposition%20leaders%20said%20they%20know%20the%20numbers%20are%20on%20government's%20side%2C%20but%20the%20aim%20of%20the%20motion%2C%20they%20said%2C%20was%20to%20compel%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20to%20speak%20on%20Manipur%20in%20the%20House%2C%20which%20would%20not%20have%20happened%20otherwise.%20MPs%20from%20the%20opposition%20INDIA%20front%20will%20visit%20Manipur%20