ppen%20continuously%20on%20both%20sides%20of%20the%20LoC.%20There%20was%20a%20complete%20wreck%20of%20houses%20and%20properties%20due%20to%20the%20shelling%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ahmad%20told%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20had%20made%20a%20wall%20using%20stones%20in%20the%20front%20of%20the%20stall%20to%20safeguard%20his%20life%20and%20the%20lives%20of%20his%20%26quot%3Bguests%26quot%3B%20while%20the%20shells%20hit%20the%20area%20around%20--%20most%20of%20which%20were%20fired%20from%20the%20nearby%20peaks%20of%20Tololing%20and%20Tiger%20Hill.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20battle%20of%20Tololing%20was%20one%20of%20the%20turning%20points%20of%20the%20Kargil%20war.%20Tololing%20peak%20is%20the%20dominant%20position%20overlooking%20the%20strategic%20Srinagar-Leh%20highway.%20Pakistani%20infiltrators%20had%20occupied%20the%20peak%20and%20it%20was%20a%20tough%20challenge%20for%20the%20Army%20to%20reclaim%20it%20as%20there%20was%20no%20cover%20for%20the%20soldiers%20and%20they%20had%20to%20fight%20in%20the%20open.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20reason%20I%20didn't%20leave%20this%20place%20during%20the%20war%20was%20that%20soldiers%20requested%20me%20not%20to%20leave.%20They%20told%20me%20if%20you%20will%20also%20leave%2C%20then%20who%20will%20give%20them%20food%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ahmad%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20media%20personnel%20were%20also%20here%20at%20that%20time%20and%20they%20also%20asked%20me%20to%20stay%20put%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Army%20provided%20him%20with%20ration%20supplies%20and%20he%20used%20to%20make%20tea%20and%20food%20for%20the%20soldiers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20very%20scary%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20when%20asked%20if%20he%20felt%20afraid.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20the%20shells%20used%20to%20explode%2C%20we%20used%20to%20shudder.%20That%20time%20was%20very%20scary.%20For%20the%20whole%20two%20months%2C%20war%20was%20being%20fought%20and%20around%20150%20to%20200%20bombs%20exploded%20daily.%20The%20pause%20was%20only%20during%20evening%20prayers.%20Other%20than%20that%2C%20it%20was%20a%20continuous%20trail%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ahmad%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20whether%20his%20family%20feared%20for%20his%20life%2C%20he%20said%20he%20used%20to%20call%20home%20from%20the%20telephone%20exchange%20booth%20to%20inform%20them%20about%20his%20well-being.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbdul%20Majeed%2C%20a%20local%2C%20in%20his%20eighties%2C%20said%20he%20has%20known%20Ahmad%20for%20over%2030%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20(Ahmad)%20did%20not%20leave%20this%20place%20when%20the%20war%20began%20and%20he%20was%20here%20till%20the%20end%20of%20the%20war.%20He%20is%20very%20courageous.%20During%20the%20time%20of%20war%2C%20he%20tirelessly%20served%20meals%20to%20the%20Army%20men.%20Even%20I%20left%2C%20and%20when%20I%20used%20to%20come%20in%20between%20to%20check%20on%20my%20house%20and%20property%20and%20livestock%2C%20I%20saw%20he%20(Ahmad)%20was%20working%20at%20his%20shop%2C%20serving%20tea%20and%20meals%20to%20the%20soldiers%2C%26quot%3B%20Majeed%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20two%20months%20of%20the%20war%2C%20Ahmad%20was%20like%20a%20friend%20to%20the%20soldiers%20and%20to%20the%20visiting%20media%20men%2C%20listened%20to%20their%20stories%2C%20felt%20their%20sadness%20as%20well%20as%20joys%2C%20and%20played%20hide-and-seek%20with%20the%20raining%20Pakistani%20shells.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20job%20was%20to%20serve%20them%20food%20only.%20The%20soldiers%20used%20to%20help%20me%20and%20even%20used%20to%20wash%20utensils%2C%26quot%3B%20Ahmad%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20Army%20had%20launched%20a%20fierce%20counter-assault%2C%20'Operation%20Vijay'%2C%20to%20push%20back%20Pakistani%20forces%20that%20had%20stealthily%20occupied%20important%20heights%20in%20Ladakh%20in%201999.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Kargil%20war%20saw%20soldiers%20of%20the%20Indian%20armed%20forces%20fight%20in%20the%20most%20challenging%20terrain%20under%20harsh%20weather%20