Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20today%2C%20Trinamool%20Congress%20MP%20Derek%20O'Brien%20directed%20a%20jab%20at%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20claiming%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20got%20you%20exactly%20where%20we%20wanted%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHello%2C%20Mr%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%20You%20are%20at%20it%20again%3F%20Attacking%20us%20with%20our%20new%20name%20INDIA%2C%20Jeetega%20Bharat.%20What's%20happened%3F%20The%20only%20response%20you%20can%20give%20is%20a%20negative%20one.%20You%20know%2C%20Mr%20Modi%2C%20we've%20got%20you%20just%20where%20we%20wanted%20you%20to%20be%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20said%20in%20a%20video%20message%20he%20posted%20on%20Twitter%2C%20responding%20to%20PM%20Modi's%20address%20in%20Rajasthan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Opposition%20coalition%2C%20PM%20Modi%20said%20today%2C%20had%20changed%20its%20name%20from%20UPA%20(United%20Progressive%20Alliance)%20to%20INDIA%20to%20hide%20its%20past%20wrongdoings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20surprise%20move%20a%20days%20before%20the%20Opposition%20meet%2C%20the%20BJP%20had%20also%20called%20a%20meeting%20in%20Delhi%20that%20coincided%20with%20it.%20In%20a%20grand%20show%20of%20strength%2C%20the%20party%20had%20gathered%20together%2038%20allies%2C%20ahead%20of%20the%20Opposition's%C2%A0%2026.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690476240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fs04rceo_opposition-grand-alliance-2023-pmo_625x300_18_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fopposition-bloc-india-to-hold-next-meeting-in-mumbai-on-august-25-26-say-sources-4246389%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20freshly%20minted%20Opposition%20bloc%20INDIA%20will%20hold%20its%20next%20meeting%20in%20Mumbai%20on%20August%2025-26%2C%20sources%20have%20told%20NDTV.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fopposition-bloc-india-to-hold-next-meeting-in-mumbai-on-august-25-26-say-sources-4246389%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fopposition-bloc-india-to-hold-next-meeting-in-mumbai-on-august-25-26-say-sources-4246389%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fopposition-bloc-india-to-hold-next-meeting-in-mumbai-on-august-25-26-say-sources-4246389%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Explainer%3A%20Pakistan%20Has%20Just%20Given%20More%20Powers%20to%20Its%20Caretaker%20Government.%20And%20It%20Is%20Not%20Good%20News%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F24215513%2F6483091829_b0a9599ab5_k.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20With%20a%20joint%20session%20of%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20parliament%20handing%20over%20more%20powers%20to%20a%20caretaker%20government%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20July%2026%2C%20questions%20are%20being%20raised%20over%20whether%20the%20general%20elections%20would%20be%20held%20in%20October%20as%20per%20the%20constitutional%20provisions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%20is%20a%20short%20explainer%20on%20why%20the%20legislative%20changes%20have%20led%20to%20concerns%20that%20elections%20will%20be%20delayed%20and%20any%20polls%20under%20the%20%E2%80%98empowered%E2%80%99%20caretaker%20government%20may%20not%20be%20an%20answer%20to%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20chronic%20political%20instability.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20the%20caretaker%20system%20of%20Pakistan%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%20general%20elections%2C%20some%20democratically%20elected%20governments%20transition%20into%20a%20%E2%80%98caretaker%E2%80%99%20mode%2C%20wherein%20their%20powers%20are%20severely%20limited.%20In%20India%2C%20a%20code%20of%20conduct%20is%20supposed%20to%20come%20into%20force%20after%20the%20Election%20Commission%20announces%20the%20poll%20dates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Pakistan%20is%20almost%20unique%20in%20institutionalising%20the%20practice%20of%20appointing%20non-elected%20officials%20to%20head%20caretaker%20governments.%20Bangladesh%20had%20also%20drawn%20up%20guidelines%20for%20caretaker%20governments%2C%20but%20the%20provision%20was%20removed%20from%20the%20constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPakistan%20has%20a%20long%20history%20of%20holding%20elections%20under%20%E2%80%9Cneutral%E2%80%9D%20candidates%2C%20but%20they%20have%20all%20been%20highly%20contentious.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202012%2C%20electoral%20reforms%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dawn.com%2Fnews%2F696880%5C%22%3Ewere%20introduced%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20removing%20the%20power%20of%20the%20president%20to%20appoint%20a%20caretaker%20prime%20minister%20or%20chief%20minister.%20The%2020th%20amendment%20established%20that%20if%20the%20prime%20minister%20and%20the%20leader%20of%20opposition%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20decide%20on%20the%20name%20of%20the%20caretaker%20prime%20minister%2C%20then%20the%20decision%20would%20be%20taken%20by%20a%20parliamentary%20committee.%20The%20committee%20is%20made%20up%20of%20equal%20number%20of%20lawmakers%20from%20the%20ruling%20side%20and%20the%20opposition.%20However%2C%20if%20the%20committee%20also%20fails%20to%20reach%20a%20decision%2C%20then%20the%20Election%20Commission%20will%20take%20the%20decision%20within%20two%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20were%20the%20powers%20of%20the%20caretaker%20government%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fna.gov.pk%2Fuploads%2Fdocuments%2F1506961151_781.pdf%5C%22%3EElection%20Act%20of%202017%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20caretaker%20government%20had%20to%20support%20the%20Election%20Commission%20in%20holding%20the%20polls%2C%20as%20well%20as%20keep%20the%20government%20ticking%20on%20a%20day-to-day%20basis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20had%20strict%20instructions%20that%20the%20caretaker%20government%20shall%2C%20as%20per%20section%20230%20(1)%2C%20%E2%80%9Crestrict%20itself%20to%20activities%20that%20are%20of%20routine%2C%20non-controversial%20and%20urgent%2C%20in%20the%20public%20interest%20and%20reversible%20by%20the%20future%20government%20elected%20after%20the%20elections%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20section%20230%20(2)%20had%20provisions%20that%20the%20interim%20government%20cannot%20take%20%E2%80%9Cmajor%20policy%20decisions%20except%20on%20urgent%20matters%E2%80%9D%20and%20neither%20enter%20into%20%E2%80%9Cmajor%20international%20negotiation%20with%20any%20foreign%20country%20or%20international%20agency%20or%20sign%20or%20ratify%20any%20international%20binding%20instrument%20except%20in%20an%20exceptional%20case%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20were%20the%20changes%20unveiled%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20month%2C%20Pakistan%20Prime%20Minister%20Shehbaz%20Sharif%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheprint.in%2Fworld%2Fwill-hand-over-charge-to-caretaker-government-in-august-pak-pm-shehbaz-sharif%2F1668529%2F%5C%22%3Eannounced%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20he%20will%20hand%20over%20the%20reins%20of%20the%20government%20to%20a%20caretaker%20government%20in%20August.%20The%20move%20immediately%20triggered%20feverish%20speculation%20over%20the%20identity%20of%20the%20caretaker%20prime%20ministers%2C%20with%20the%20politicking%20taking%20place%20in%20Dubai%20and%20London%20where%20the%20heads%20of%20the%20ruling%20coalition%20are%20camped.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20a%20slew%20of%20reports%20that%20claimed%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dawn.com%2Fnews%2F1766399%2Fn-proposes-dar-as-interim-pm-but-ppp-disagrees%5C%22%3Efinance%20minister%20Ishaq%20Dar%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%93%20whose%20son%20is%20married%20to%20Pakistan%20Muslim%20League%20(Nawaz)%20party%20chief%20Nawaz%20Sharif%E2%80%99s%20daughter%20%E2%80%93%20would%20be%20the%20head%20of%20the%20caretaker%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIncidentally%2C%20the%20current%20Leader%20of%20Opposition%20in%20the%20National%20Assembly%20is%20a%20Pakistan%20Tehreek-e-Insaf%20(PTI)%20dissident%20lawmaker%2C%20who%20had%20been%20part%20of%2020%20PTI%20members%20that%20had%20joined%20the%20opposition%20in%20passing%20a%20no-confidence%20motion%20against%20then%20Prime%20Minister%20Imran%20Khan%20in%20March%202022.%20Therefore%2C%20the%20choice%20for%20heading%20the%20caretaker%20government%20would%20be%20an%20exercise%20for%20the%20ruling%20parties%2C%20despite%20the%20guidelines%20on%20paper.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDar%E2%80%99s%20name%20was%20quickly%20shot%20down%20by%20the%20Pakistan%20People%E2%80%99s%20Party.%20Nevertheless%2C%20Pakistan%20came%20to%20know%20about%20the%20impending%20changes%20to%20the%20powers%20of%20the%20caretaker%20government%20only%20from%20his%20appearance%20on%20a%20television%20channel.%20When%20asked%20whether%20section%20230%20of%20the%20Election%20Act%20would%20be%20modified%2C%20he%20replied%2C%20%E2%80%9CTo%20the%20best%20of%20my%20understanding%2C%20yes.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fpakistan-india-imran-khan-manipur-karnataka%5C%22%3EFrom%20Pakistan%2C%20a%20Message%20for%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20was%20the%20amendment%20passed%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Pakistan%20government%20on%20July%2025%20proposed%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftribune.com.pk%2Fstory%2F2427955%2F54-amendments-proposed-to-election-act%5C%22%3E54%20amendments%20to%20the%20Election%20Act%2C%202017%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20including%20upgrading%20the%20powers%20that%20will%20allow%20the%20caretaker%20government%20to%20take%20decisions%20with%20regard%20to%20the%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20government%20was%20forced%20to%20defer%20the%20passage%20of%20the%20Bill%20by%20a%20day%20when%20both%20political%20allies%20and%20the%20opposition%20claimed%20at%20the%20joint%20session%20of%20parliament%20that%20there%20was%20a%20last%20minute%20addition%20to%20the%20clause%20that%20would%20enlarge%20the%20scope%20of%20the%20powers%20of%20the%20caretaker%20government%20to%20decide%20on%20%E2%80%9Curgent%20matters%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20of%20the%20opposing%20lawmakers%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20new%20changes%20were%20not%20even%20discussed%20in%20the%20closed-door%20meetings%20of%20the%20parliamentary%20committee%20on%20electoral%20reforms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20ahead%20of%20the%20Wednesday%20(July%2026)%20meeting%2C%20the%20parliamentary%20committee%20met%20with%20the%20government%20and%20was%20able%20to%20persuade%20its%20allies%2C%20with%20a%20slightly%20altered%20amendment.%20However%2C%20the%20opposition%20remained%20unconvinced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftribune.com.pk%2Fstory%2F2427994%2Fjoint-session-approves-election-act-amendments-empowering-caretaker-setup%5C%22%3EThe%20%3Cem%3EExpress%20Tribune%3C%2Fem%3E%20described%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20passage%20of%20the%20Bill%20by%20a%20voice%20vote%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Cstunning%20display%20of%20legislative%20acrobatics%E2%80%9D%20that%20has%20re-drawn%20the%20lines%20of%20political%20authority%20in%20Pakistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20does%20the%20amendment%20say%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDue%20to%20the%20outcry%20in%20parliament%2C%20Pakistan%20law%20minister%20Azam%20Nazeer%20Tarar%20admitted%20at%20the%20start%20of%20the%20joint%20sitting%20of%20parliament%20that%20the%20amendment%20had%20not%20been%20discussed%20during%20the%20meeting%20of%20the%20parliamentary%20committee%2C%20but%20claimed%20that%20it%20was%20posted%20on%20the%20panel%E2%80%99s%20WhatsApp%20group%20five%20days%20earlier.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20law%20minister%20said%20that%20amendment%20still%20allows%20the%20caretaker%20government%20to%20address%20%E2%80%9Curgent%20matters%E2%80%9D%2C%20but%20has%20dropped%20the%20provision%20on%20allowing%20transfers%20and%20promotions%2C%20following%20the%20strong%20objections%20raised%20earlier%20on%20Wednesday%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20approved%20amendment%2C%20as%20per%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dawn.com%2Fnews%2F1767041%2Fhue-and-cry-leads-govt-to-dilute-powers-for-caretakers%5C%22%3Emedia%20reports%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20adds%20a%20rider%20to%20section%20230(2)%3A%20%E2%80%9CProvided%20that%20sub-sections%20(1)%20and%20(2)%20shall%20not%20apply%20where%20the%20caretaker%20government%20has%20to%20take%20actions%20or%20decisions%20regarding%20existing%20bilateral%20or%20multilateral%20agreements%20or%20the%20projects%20already%20initiated%20under%20the%20Public%20Private%20Partnership%20Authority%20Act%2C%202017%20(VIII%20of%202017)%2C%20the%20Inter-Governmental%20Commercial%20Transactions%20Act%2C%202022%20(XXX%20of%202022)%20and%20the%20Privatisation%20Commission%20Ordinance%2C%202000%20(LII%20of%202000).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20sub-sections%20had%20outlined%20the%20limitations%20of%20the%20powers%20of%20the%20caretaker%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fpakistans-precarious-path-from-hero-worship-to-economic-desperation%5C%22%3EPakistan%E2%80%99s%20Precarious%20Path%3A%20From%20Hero%20Worship%20to%20Economic%20Desperation%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20the%20official%20argument%20for%20%E2%80%98empowering%E2%80%99%20the%20caretaker%20government%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20month%2C%20the%20International%20Monetary%20Fund%E2%80%99s%20(IMF)%20board%20approved%20a%20nine-month%20standby%20arrangement%20for%20%243%20billion%2C%20which%20has%20since%20opened%20more%20doors%20to%20bilateral%20donors.%20During%20the%20joint%20session%2C%20the%20Pakistani%20law%20minister%20claimed%20that%20giving%20more%20powers%20to%20the%20caretaker%20government%20would%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.geo.tv%2Flatest%2F501392-pml-ns-move-seeking-unbridled-powers-for-caretakers-faces-opposition-from-allies%5C%22%3Eensure%20the%20continuity%20of%20measures%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20were%20agreed%20upon%20with%20the%20IMF%20as%20the%20same%20could%20not%20be%20put%20in%20cold%20storage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJamaat-I-Islami%20senator%20Senator%20Mushtaq%20Ahmed%20claimed%20that%20it%20was%20regrettable%20that%20the%20IMF%20was%20even%20influencing%20electoral%20laws.%20He%20described%20it%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Csoft%20coup%E2%80%9D%2C%20that%20put%20question%20marks%20on%20the%20conduct%20of%20the%20general%20elections.%20Ahmed%20also%20articulated%20that%20the%20insidious%20reason%20for%20the%20amendment%20might%20be%20to%20delay%20the%20elections%20by%20extending%20the%20term%20of%20the%20caretaker%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPakistan%E2%80%99s%20minister%20for%20economic%20affairs%2C%20Sardar%20Ayaz%20Sadiq%2C%20dismissed%20the%20allegation%20that%20it%20would%20mean%20that%20the%20caretaker%20government%20would%20remain%20at%20the%20helm%20for%20a%20longer%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20argued%20that%20the%20powers%20of%20the%20caretakers%20under%20the%20re-drafted%20amendment%20had%20been%20restricted%20to%20ongoing%20multilateral%20and%20bilateral%20projects%2C%20and%20they%20would%20not%20have%20the%20mandate%20to%20initiate%20new%20projects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20has%20been%20the%20reception%20to%20the%20move%20to%20a%20Caretaker%20government%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98empowerment%E2%80%99%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20editorial%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20News%3C%2Fem%3E%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20talk%20about%20the%20name%20of%20PML-N%E2%80%99s%20Ishaq%20Dar%20and%20others%20had%20started%20to%20gather%20momentum%20when%20the%20ruling%20Pakistan%20Democratic%20Movement%20(PDM)%20coalition%20realised%20that%20the%20interim%20government%20could%20be%20prolonged%20for%20than%20the%2060%20or%2090%20days%20it%20is%20supposed%20to%20remain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20important%20to%20note%20that%20there%20is%20little%20justification%20for%20the%20whole%20constitution%20to%20be%20upended%20for%20the%20mere%20possibility%20that%20the%20interim%20setup%20could%20continue%20beyond%20its%20mandated%20time%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20newspaper.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20editorial%20criticised%20the%20ruling%20coalition%20for%20going%20back%20on%20its%20position%20enshrined%20in%20the%202006%20Charter%20of%20Democracy%2C%20which%20advocated%20for%20neutral%20caretaker%20governments%20to%20conduct%20elections%2C%20by%20having%20a%20politician%20to%20head%20the%20interim%20set-up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20prolonged%20caretaker%20setup%20has%20no%20constitutional%20justification%20%E2%80%93%20which%20is%20why%20on%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20list%20of%20things%20to%20do%20at%20the%20moment%20should%20be%3A%20a%20neutral%20caretaker%20setup%2C%20and%20free%20and%20fair%20elections.%20Everything%20else%20falls%20into%20place%20after%20that%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20editorial.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dawn.com%2Fnews%2F1766897%2Fcaretaker-conundrum%5C%22%3EWriting%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3EDawn%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Zahid%20Hussain%20wrote%20that%20two%20months%20were%20not%20a%20long%20period%20that%20%E2%80%9Cpolicy%20decisions%20cannot%20wait%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20move%20also%20fuels%20speculation%20about%20elections%20not%20being%20held%20within%20the%20stipulated%20time%20frame.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWarning%20that%20their%20alignment%20with%20the%20security%20establishment%20to%20dismantle%20PTI%20will%20haunt%20the%20political%20parties%2C%20Hussain%20noted%20that%20tainted%20elections%20under%20a%20partisan%20caretaker%20administration%20will%20aggravate%20an%20already%20combustible%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CUnfortunately%2C%20the%20elections%2C%20which%20are%20supposed%20to%20strengthen%20the%20democratic%20process%20and%20provide%20political%20stability%2C%20may%20result%20in%20the%20country%20plunging%20deeper%20into%20chaos%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMudassar%20Rizvi%2C%20who%20has%20been%20associated%20with%20the%20watchdog%20Free%20and%20Fair%20Election%20Network%20(Fafen)%2C%20wrote%20that%20the%20political%20consequences%20of%20this%20amendment%20and%20the%20delay%20in%20holding%20elections%20to%20Punjab%20and%20Khyber%20Pakhtunkhwa%20assemblies%20beyond%2090%20days%20%E2%80%9Chave%20reinforced%20the%20view%20that%20efforts%20are%20afoot%20to%20put%20together%20a%20caretaker%20dispensation%20with%20an%20aim%20greater%20than%20simply%20holding%20the%20next%20general%20elections%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690476231000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F24215513%2F6483091829_b0a9599ab5_k.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fexplainer-pakistan-has-just-given-more-powers-to-its-caretaker-government-and-it-is-not-good-news%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Why%20the%20legislative%20changes%20have%20led%20to%20concerns%20that%20elections%20will%20be%20delayed%20and%20any%20polls%20under%20the%20%E2%80%98empowered%E2%80%99%20caretaker%20government%20may%20not%20be%20an%20answer%20to%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20chronic%20political%20instability.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fexplainer-pakistan-has-just-given-more-powers-to-its-caretaker-government-and-it-is-not-good-news%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22On%20Shubman%20Gill's%20Poor%20Show%20In%20WI%2C%20Ex-India%20Star%20Points%20Out%20Loopholes%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFormer%20India%20batter%20WV%20Raman%20highlighted%20two%20aspects%20that%20youngster%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Shubman%20Gill%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F108578-shubman-gill-playerprofile%5C%22%3EShubman%20Gill%3C%2Fa%3E%20needs%20to%20work%20on%20to%20consistently%20score%20runs%20in%20the%20longest%20format%20of%20the%20game.%20Despite%20cementing%20his%20place%20in%20the%20Indian%20team%20in%20all%20three%20formats%2C%20Gill%20has%20failed%20to%20impress%20experts%20and%20fans%20with%20his%20batting%20in%20the%20longest%20format%20of%20the%20game.%20The%2023-year-old%20averages%2065.55%20in%20ODIs%2C%2040.40%20in%20T20Is%2C%20but%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20Test%20cricket%2C%20he%20only%20averages%2019.%20In%20the%20recently%20concluded%20Test%20series%2C%20Gill%20failed%20to%20get%20beyond%2029%20in%20three%20innings.%20Even%20in%20the%20first%20ODI%2C%20Gill%20was%20out%20for%207.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaman%20feels%20'hurried%20sideways%20trigger'%20and%20over-reliance%20on%20bottom-hand%20stroke%20making%20have%20been%20the%20reasons%20behind%20his%20lack%20of%20runs%20in%20the%20longest%20format.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20found%20he%20was%20making%20too%20much%20trigger%20movement%20sideways.%20It%20was%20also%20a%20bit%20quick.%20What%20could%20result%20from%20it%20is%2C%20you%20will%20have%20real%20good%20days%20and%20real%20bad%20days.%20On%20some%20days%20the%20trigger%20movement%20will%20be%20in%20sync%20or%20bowling%20will%20be%20such%20that%20it%20will%20help%20you%20get%20runs.%20And%20on%20certain%20days%20the%20movements%20will%20be%20disconnected%20with%20what%20is%20being%20required%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fwhy-is-shubman-gills-test-average-not-good-rapid-sideways-trigger-and-bottom-hand-domination-says-wv-raman-8860098%2F%5C%22%3ERaman%20told%20The%20Indian%20Express.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLot%20of%20batters%20of%20late%20allow%20the%20bottom%20hand%20to%20dominate%20their%20pick%20up%20and%20down%20swing.%20Such%20batters%20will%20struggle%20against%20the%20incoming%20delivery%20because%20primarily%20their%20bat%20will%20be%20going%20across%20their%20body%2C%20the%20path%20of%20the%20bat%20will%20be%20a%20horizontal%20swing%20rather%20than%20a%20vertical%20swing.%20Let's%20say%20on%20a%20clock%20face%2C%20the%20bat%20swing%20will%20be%2010-4.%20It%20won't%20be%2012%20to%206.%20Some%20will%20have%2011-5%2C%20some%20have%2010-4%20and%20in%20some%20exaggerated%20cases%20between%209-10%20and%203-4.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBottom%20hand%20domination%20is%20not%20going%20to%20help%20you%20tackle%20the%20incoming%20ball%20because%20it%20will%20be%20a%20case%20of%20bat%20going%20across%20the%20body%20and%20the%20bat%20face%20will%20be%20closed%20and%20thereby%20giving%20minimal%20chance%20for%20bat%20coming%20to%20contact%20with%20the%20ball%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20white-ball%20cricket%2C%20Gill%20has%20evolved%20into%20one%20of%20the%20most%20explosive%20batters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20this%20year's%20IPL%2C%20he%20amassed%20851%20runs%20for%20Gujarat%20Titans.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690475760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Ffpehhgc8_gill-afp_625x300_27_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fwest-indies-vs-india-2023%2Fon-shubman-gills-poor-show-in-west-indies-tests-ex-india-stars-points-out-flaws-4240575%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Shubman%20Gill%20averages%2065.55%20in%20ODIs%2C%2040.40%20in%20T20Is%2C%20but%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20Test%20cricket%2C%20he%20only%20averages%2019.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fwest-indies-vs-india-2023%2Fon-shubman-gills-poor-show-in-west-indies-tests-ex-india-stars-points-out-flaws-4240575%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fwest-indies-vs-india-2023%2Fon-shubman-gills-poor-show-in-west-indies-tests-ex-india-stars-points-out-flaws-4240575%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fwest-indies-vs-india-2023%2Fon-shubman-gills-poor-show-in-west-indies-tests-ex-india-stars-points-out-flaws-4240575%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22What%20PM%20Modi%2C%20Xi%20Jinping%20Spoke%20About%20After%20Shaking%20Hands%20At%202022%20G20%20Dinner%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20Chinese%20President%20Xi%20Jinping%20had%20exchanged%20courtesies%20and%20spoke%20on%20the%20need%20to%20stabilise%20the%20bilateral%20relations%20at%20a%20dinner%20during%20the%20G20%20summit%20in%20Bali%20last%20year%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20(MEA)%20said%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20days%20ago%2C%20the%20Chinese%20foreign%20ministry%20following%20a%20meeting%20between%20NSA%20Ajit%20Doval%20and%20top%20Chinese%20diplomat%20Wang%20Yi%20in%20Johannesburg%20claimed%20that%20Xi%20and%20PM%20Modi%20had%20reached%20an%20%26quot%3Bimportant%20consensus%26quot%3B%20on%20stabilising%20bilateral%20ties%20at%20the%20interaction%20on%20the%20margins%20of%20the%20G20%20Summit%20last%20November.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDuring%20the%20Bali%20G20%20summit%20last%20year%2C%20the%20prime%20minister%20and%20President%20Xi%20Jinping%20at%20the%20conclusion%20of%20that%20dinner%20hosted%20by%20the%20Indonesian%20President%20exchanged%20courtesies%20and%20spoke%20of%20the%20need%20to%20stabilise%20our%20bilateral%20relations%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Bagchi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20you%20are%20aware%2C%20we%20have%20steadfastly%20maintained%20the%20key%20to%20resolution%20of%20the%20whole%20issue%20is%20to%20resolve%20the%20situation%20along%20the%20LAC%20(Line%20of%20Actual%20Control)%20on%20the%20Western%20sector%20of%20India-China%20boundary%20and%20to%20restore%20peace%20and%20tranquillity%20in%20the%20border%20areas%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20comments%20came%20when%20asked%20about%20China's%20claim%20of%20the%20consensus%20reached%20at%20the%20interaction%20between%20the%20two%20top%20leaders%20in%20Bali.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20brief%20interaction%20between%20PM%20Modi%20and%20Xi%20in%20Bali%2C%20the%20MEA%20had%20said%20they%20exchanged%20courtesies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20their%20first%20such%20exchanges%20in%20public%20view%20since%20the%20India-China%20border%20standoff%20began%20in%20May%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Doval%20met%20Wang%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20the%20BRICS%20NSAs'%20meeting%20in%20Johannesburg%20on%20July%2024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20statement%20on%20the%20meeting%2C%20the%20MEA%20said%20Doval%20conveyed%20that%20the%20situation%20along%20the%20LAC%20in%20the%20western%20sector%20of%20the%20India-China%20boundary%20since%202020%20had%20%26quot%3Beroded%20strategic%20trust%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20public%20and%20political%20basis%20of%20the%20relationship.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20said%20the%20NSA%20emphasised%20the%20importance%20of%20continuing%20efforts%20to%20fully%20resolve%20the%20situation%20and%20restore%20peace%20and%20tranquillity%20in%20the%20border%20areas%20so%20as%20to%20remove%20impediments%20to%20normalcy%20in%20bilateral%20ties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20two%20sides%20agreed%20that%20the%20India-China%20bilateral%20relationship%20is%20significant%20not%20only%20for%20the%20two%20countries%20but%20also%20for%20the%20region%20and%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20MEA%20said%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20and%20Chinese%20troops%20are%20locked%20in%20an%20over%20three-year%20standoff%20in%20certain%20friction%20points%20in%20eastern%20Ladakh%20even%20as%20the%20two%20sides%20completed%20disengagement%20from%20several%20areas%20following%20extensive%20diplomatic%20and%20military%20talks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20refers%20to%20eastern%20Ladakh%20as%20Western%20sector.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ties%20between%20the%20two%20countries%20nosedived%20significantly%20following%20the%20fierce%20clash%20in%20the%20Galwan%20Valley%20in%20June%202020%20that%20marked%20the%20most%20serious%20military%20conflict%20between%20the%20two%20sides%20in%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20whether%20the%20Chinese%20president%20would%20attend%20the%20G20%20summit%20in%20Delhi%2C%20Mr%20Bagchi%20said%20India%20is%20making%20all%20efforts%20and%20preparations%20for%20its%20success%20with%20the%20participation%20of%20all%20invited%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20India's%20proposal%20to%20make%20the%20African%20Union%20a%20permanent%20member%20of%20the%20G20%2C%20he%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20hope%20this%20does%20happen.%26quot%3B%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20he%20added%20that%20it%20would%20be%20premature%20to%20say%20anything%20specific%20on%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20Russian%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin's%20reported%20comments%20supporting%20the%20proposal%2C%20Bagchi%20said%20he%20has%20not%20seen%20the%20remarks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BIf%20Russia%20has%20supported%20(the%20proposal)%2C%20it%20is%20good.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690475400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fv3kbuuf8_pm-modi-xi-jinping-bali-ani_625x300_27_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhat-pm-narendra-modi-china-xi-jinping-spoke-about-after-shaking-hands-at-2022-g20-dinner-4246136%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20Chinese%20President%20Xi%20Jinping%20had%20exchanged%20courtesies%20and%20spoke%20on%20the%20need%20to%20stabilise%20the%20bilateral%20relations%20at%20a%20dinner%20during%20the%20G20%20summit%20in%20Bali%20last%20year%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20(MEA)%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fin