ning%20to%20move%20back%20to%20the%20US.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20tweet%2C%20he%20also%C2%A0compared%20the%20learning%20experience%20in%20the%20Bay%20Area%20(San%20Francisco)%20to%20his%20struggles%20with%20company%20registration%20in%20India%20and%20cited%20specific%20reasons%20for%20his%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''Love%20Bangalore%20%2F%20India%2C%20but%20I%20have%20learned%20more%20in%20the%20last%203%20days%20in%20Bay%20Area%20than%20I%20could%20in%20a%20month%20back%20home.%20Spent%202%20months%20just%20trying%20to%20register%20a%20co%20in%20India%20%26amp%3B%20it's%20still%20not%20done.%20The%20problem-solution%20feedback%20loop%20from%20potential%20customers%2C%20Investors%20%26amp%3B%20even%20fellow%20founders%20is%20at%20a%20different%20level.%20The%20time%20may%20be%20coming%20for%20me%20to%20move%20back%20to%20the%20US.%20And%20I%20say%20this%20with%20a%20heavy%20heart%2C''%20he%20wrote%20in%20the%20tweet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESee%20the%20tweet%20here%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3ELove%20Bangalore%20%2F%20India%2C%20but%20I%20have%20learnt%20more%20in%20last%203%20days%20in%20Bay%20Area%20than%20I%20could%20in%20a%20month%20back%20home.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnSpent%202%20months%20just%20to%20try%20to%20register%20a%20co%20in%20India%20%26amp%3B%20it's%20still%20not%20done.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnProblem%20-%20solution%20feedback%20loop%20from%20potential%20customers%2C%20Investors%20%26amp%3B%20even%20fellow%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Brij%20Singh%20(%40brijbhasin)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fbrijbhasin%2Fstatus%2F1684404475870474243%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJuly%2027%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20his%C2%A0Linkedin%20profile%2C%20Brij%20Singh%20has%20been%20working%20in%20the%20technology%20and%20finance%20sector%20in%20India%20and%20the%20US%20for%2018%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20reply%20to%20another%20Twitter%20user%2C%20he%20added%20that%20he%20was%20not%20giving%20up%20on%20Bengaluru%20entirely%20was%20just%20''stating%20facts.''%20He%C2%A0acknowledged%20the%20advantages%20of%20building%20a%20company%20in%20India%20for%20a%20global%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''Umm%20not%20giving%20up%20on%20anything.%20Just%20stating%20the%20facts.%20There%20are%20lot%20of%20advantages%20in%20building%20from%20India%20for%20the%20world%20as%20well.%20One%20must%20learn%20to%20leverage%20whatever%20opportunities%20they%20can%20to%20execute%20and%20compete%20in%20a%20global%20market.%20That%20is%20the%20reality%2C''%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EUmm%20not%20giving%20up%20on%20anything.%20Just%20stating%20the%20facts.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThere%20are%20lot%20of%20advantages%20in%20building%20from%20India%20for%20the%20world%20as%20well.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnOne%20must%20learn%20to%20leverage%20whatever%20opportunities%20they%20can%20to%20execute%20and%20compete%20in%20a%20global%20market.%20That%20is%20the%20reality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Brij%20Singh%20(%40brijbhasin)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fbrijbhasin%2Fstatus%2F1684442295079407617%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJuly%2027%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20some%20supported%20his%20decision%2C%20others%20encouraged%20him%20to%20try%20a%20little%20more%20and%20change%20his%20strategy.%20Some%20shared%20similar%20struggles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20user%20said%2C%20''Why%20would%20it%20take%202%20months%3F%20I%20formed%20my%20LLP%20in%20a%20week.%20You%20have%20an%20issue%20of%20bad%20CA.%20Quite%20frankly%20you%20can%20register%20a%20company%20yourself%20and%20don't%20even%20need%20a%20CA.%20Takes%20a%20couple%20of%20days%20max.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E