%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-325389%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EShe%20has%20also%20helped%2021%20artists%20sell%20their%20work%20online%20and%20in%20onsite%20exhibitions.%20Picture%20credit%3A%20Tarini%20Malhotra%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharad%20Preet%20Singh%2C%20the%20team%20lead%20and%20manager%20of%20the%20company%20who%20trained%20Aditya%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20he%20joined%2C%20I%20was%20very%20nervous%20and%20a%20little%20unsure%20of%20how%20he%20would%20fit%20in%20here.%20But%20to%20my%20surprise%2C%20it%20was%20not%20so%20difficult%20to%20incubate%20him.%20Aditya%20is%20a%20hardworking%20individual%20and%20was%20able%20to%20adapt%20to%20everything%20at%20a%20good%20pace%2C%20which%20is%20why%20we%20even%20extended%20his%20internship%20and%20gave%20him%20extra%20benefits.%20I%20think%20this%20is%20a%20great%20initiative%20and%20look%20forward%20to%20seeing%20more%20inclusivity%20at%20workplaces%20all%20across%20the%20country.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20how%20she%20comes%20in%20contact%20with%20the%20neurodivergent%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20neurodivergent%20community%20is%20quite%20close-knit%20and%20always%20in%20touch.%20Most%20times%2C%20people%20hear%20about%20us%20from%20someone%20and%20show%20up%20on%20their%20own%20looking%20for%20work.%20If%20we%20are%20not%20approached%2C%20then%20we%20also%20have%20tie-ins%20with%20six%20other%20NGOs%20in%20and%20around%20Delhi%20NCR%20region%20who%20help%20us%20reach%20the%20remotest%20person%20who%20may%20need%20help.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSince%20I%20was%20a%20child%2C%20my%20parents%20and%20teachers%20have%20motivated%20me%20to%20find%20solutions%20to%20societal%20problems.%20I%E2%80%99ve%20always%20understood%20that%20regardless%20of%20my%20chosen%20career%2C%20improving%20society%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.