uesday's%20meeting.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20his%20address%20in%20Rajasthan%20today%2C%20PM%20Modi%20said%20the%20opposition%20coalition%20had%20changed%20its%20name%20from%20the%20United%20Progressive%20Alliance%20(UPA)%20to%20INDIA%20to%20hide%20its%20past%20wrongdoings.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20(opposition)%20changed%20their%20name%20from%20the%20UPA%20to%20INDIA%20to%20hide%20how%20they%20schemed%20against%20the%20poor.%20They%20have%20changed%20their%20name%20so%20that%20they%20can%20remove%20the%20stain%20of%20capitulating%20to%20terror.%20Their%20ways%20are%20similar%20to%20that%20of%20the%20country's%20enemy.%20The%20name%20INDIA%20is%20not%20to%20show%20their%20patriotism%2C%20but%20with%20an%20intention%20to%20rob%20the%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690463640000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2021-12%2Fqodbf438_derek-obrien-rajya-sabha-ani_625x300_21_December_21.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fon-india-name-weve-got-pm-exactly-where-we-wanted-him-derek-obrien-4245674%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Trinamool%20Congress%20MP%20Derek%20O'Brien%20has%20launched%20a%20sharp%20attack%20on%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20for%20his%20jibes%20against%20the%20opposition%20alliance's%20INDIA%20name%2C%20saying%20they%20have%20the%20PM%20exactly%20where%20they%20wanted%20him%20to%20be.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fon-india-name-weve-got-pm-exactly-where-we-wanted-him-derek-obrien-4245674%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fon-india-name-weve-got-pm-exactly-where-we-wanted-him-derek-obrien-4245674%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fon-india-name-weve-got-pm-exactly-where-we-wanted-him-derek-obrien-4245674%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22World's%20Largest%20Museum%2C%20Delhi's%20Yuge%20Yugeen%20Bharat%2C%20To%20Have%20950%20Rooms%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20upcoming%20Yuge%20Yugeen%20Bharat%20National%20Museum%20-%20billed%20to%20be%20the%20largest%20museum%20in%20the%20world%20-%20will%20have%20eight%20thematic%20segments%20telling%20the%20story%20of%20India%20spanning%20over%205%2C000%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20museum%2C%20housed%20in%20the%20North%20and%20South%20blocks%20in%20the%20heart%20of%20the%20country's%20capital%2C%20will%20cover%20an%20area%20of%201.17%20lakh%20sqm%20with%20950%20rooms%20spread%20over%20a%20basement%20and%20three%20storeys%2C%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20occasion%20of%20the%20International%20Museum%20Day%20on%20May%2018%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20had%20launched%20a%20virtual%20walkthrough%20of%20the%20upcoming%20museum%20after%20inaugurating%20a%20three-day%20International%20Museum%20Expo%20at%20Pragati%20Maidan%20in%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday%20evening%2C%20PM%20Modi%20inaugurated%20the%20International%20Exhibition-cum-Convention%20Centre%20(IECC)%20complex%2C%20developed%20at%20a%20cost%20of%20about%20Rs%202%2C700%20crore%20with%20a%20campus%20area%20of%20approximately%20123%20acres%2C%20and%20unveiled%20its%20new%20name%20-%20Bharat%20Mandapam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20his%20address%20at%20the%20inauguration%2C%20PM%20Modi%20also%20announced%20Yuge%20Yugeen%20Bharat%20National%20Museum.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20museum%20will%20have%20%26quot%3Beight%20thematic%20segments%26quot%3B%20and%20will%20showcase%20the%20rich%20civilisational%20culture%20of%20India%20spanning%20over%205%2C000%20years%2C%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20segments%20broadly%20include%20ancient%20Indian%20knowledge%2C%20ancient%20to%20medieval%2C%20medieval%2C%20medieval%20to%20transition%20phase%2C%20modern%20India%2C%20the%20colonial%20rule%20(when%20the%20Dutch%2C%20the%20British%2C%20the%20Portuguese%20and%20others%20came%20to%20India)%2C%20the%20freedom%20struggle%20and%20the%20100%20years%20from%201947%20onwards%2Cincluding%20the%20vision%20ahead%2C%20the%20senior%20official%20told%20PTI.%20It%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bforward-looking%20museum%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20virtual%20walkthrough%20of%20the%20museum%20provides%20a%20digital%20experience%20into%20how%20the%20galleries%20and%20gardens%20in%20it%20will%20appear%20once%20the%20museum%20is%20completed.%20It%20showed%20that%20the%20galleries%20through%20exhibits%20will%20inform%20the%20visitor%20about%20ancient%20town%20planning%20systems%2C%20the%20Vedas%2C%20Upanishads%2C%20ancient%20medical%20knowledge%2C%20etc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMauryan%20to%20Gupta%20Empires%2C%20Vijayanagara%20Empire%2C%20Mughal%20Empire%2C%20and%20the%20rule%20of%20several%20other%20dynasties%20are%20mentioned%20in%20the%20walkthrough.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAncient%20artefacts%20and%20other%20rich%20collections%20of%20the%20National%20Museum%2C%20located%20on%20Janpath%20here%2C%20are%20planned%20to%20be%20shifted%20to%20the%20buildings%20of%20the%20North%20and%20South%20Blocks%20as%20part%20of%20the%20project%2C%20a%20senior%20official%20had%20said%20earlier.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20South%20Block%20houses%20the%20External%20Affairs%20Ministry%2C%20the%20Defence%20Ministry%20and%20the%20Prime%20Minister's%20Office%2C%20while%20the%20North%20Block%20has%20the%20ministries%20of%20finance%20and%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnion%20Minister%20of%20State%20for%20Culture%20Meenakashi%20Lekhi%20has%20said%20that%20the%20current%20National%20Museum%20building%20will%20become%20part%20of%20the%20Kartavya%20Path%20and%20the%20annexes%20of%20the%20Kartavya%20Path.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20foundation%20of%20the%20present%20National%20Museum%20building%20was%20laid%20by%20first%20Prime%20Minister%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20on%20May%2012%2C%201955.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Kartavya%20Path%2C%20previously%20called%20Rajpath%2C