mic%20community%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20academics%20have%20said%20in%20their%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fraiot.in%2Fwhy-we-need-to-defend-prof-kham-khan-suan-hausing%2F%5C%22%3Estatement%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20indeed%20most%20unfortunate%20that%20his%20views%20%E2%80%94%20based%20on%20considered%20opinion%20and%20professional%20investigations%20%E2%80%94%20have%20been%20construed%20as%20criminal%20by%20individuals%20outside%20the%20academic%20community.%20While%20we%20believe%20that%20our%20research%20work%20has%20to%20engage%20with%20a%20non-academic%20audience%2C%20we%20are%20deeply%20troubled%20by%20the%20disproportionate%20and%20facetious%20response%20that%20his%20views%20have%20generated%20among%20a%20section%20of%20the%20wider%20public.%C2%A0%20The%20filing%20of%20criminal%20complaints%20against%20academics%20who%20share%20their%20views%20in%20the%20public%20sphere%20sets%20a%20dangerous%20precedent.%20It%20paves%20the%20way%20for%20unwarranted%20censorship%20of%20speech%2C%20thought%2C%20and%20democratic%20exchange%20of%20views.%20As%20professionals%20who%20work%20and%20write%20about%20issues%20in%20Northeast%20India%2C%20we%20feel%20that%20such%20actions%20tantamount%20to%20the%20erosion%20of%20safe%20spaces%20for%20academic%20research.%20It%20will%20hamper%20the%20intellectual%20growth%20and%20exchange%20of%20ideas%2C%20not%20just%20among%20our%20peers%2C%20but%20also%20among%20the%20next%20generation%20of%20scholars%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20continue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESignatories%20of%20the%20statement%20are%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EProf.%20Manoranjan%20Mohanty%2C%20former%20Professor%20of%20Political%20Science%2C%20University%20of%20Delhi%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EProf.%20Joy%20Pachuau.%20Centre%20for%20Historical%20Studies%2C%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20University%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EProf%20Dolly%20Kikon%2C%20School%20of%20Social%20and%20Political%20Sciences%2C%20University%20of%20Melbourne%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EDr.%20Char