Cp%3EThe%20violence%20broke%20out%20in%20Churachandpur%2C%20a%20town%20just%20south%20of%20the%20state%20capital%20Imphal%2C%20on%20May%203%2C%20following%20a%20Kuki-led%20tribal%20solidarity%20march%20in%20ten%20of%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%3Cb%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3Esixteen%20districts.%C2%A0As%20the%20Meitei%20organised%20counter-protests%20and%20blockades%2C%C2%A0clashes%20spread%20across%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWomen%C2%A0were%20part%20of%C2%A0some%20of%20the%C2%A0mobs.%20In%20some%20cases%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fmanipur-army-uses-drones-to-monitor-mobs-of-women-who-are-blocking-roads%5C%22%3Ethey%20blocked%20soldiers%20trying%20to%20intervene%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20in%20order%20to%20shield%20Meitei%20men%20conducting%20attacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThousands%C2%A0have%20been%20injured%20and%20more%20than%C2%A060%2C000%C2%A0displaced%20in%20the%20violence%3B%20more%C2%A0than%2012%2C000%20have%20fled%20to%20the%20neighbouring%20Mizoram%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHundreds%20of%20houses%2C%20places%20of%20worship%20and%20vehicles%20have%20been%20vandalised%2C%C2%A0and%C2%A0thousands%C2%A0of%20weapons%20stolen%20from%20government%20armouries.%C2%A0Arson%C2%A0and%20other%20attacks%20continue%20unabated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENumerous%20serious%20cases%20of%20sexual%20violence%20by%20Meitei%20men%2C%20militias%20and%20militants%20against%20Kuki%20women%20have%20also%20been%20reported%2C%20and%20all%20available%20evidence%20points%20to%20the%20widespread%20use%20of%20sexual%20violence%20as%20part%20of%20the%20ethnic%20conflict.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFake%20news%20about%20a%20Meitei%20woman%E2%80%99s%20rape%20in%20a%20Kuki-dominated%20area%C2%A0provoked%20a%20violent%20reaction%20from%20the%20Meitei%20community.%20A%20video%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fmanipur-video-two-kuki-women-paraded-naked-gang-raped%5C%22%3Ewent%20viral%20online%20on%20July%2019%3C%2Fa%3E%20showing%20a%20mob%20of%20Meitei%20men%20parad