ts%20and%20the%20mostly%20Christian%20Kukis%20living%20in%20the%20surrounding%20hills.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20477px)%2085vw%2C%20477px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F27113924%2FManipur-relief-map.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22477%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F27113924%2FManipur-relief-map.jpg%20919w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F27113924%2FManipur-relief-map-286x300.jpg%20286w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-665392%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ERelief%20map%20of%20Manipur.%20The%20Imphal%20valley%20is%20seen%20in%20the%20centre.%20Photo%3A%20Milenioscuro%2FWikimedia%20Commons.%20CC%20BY-SA%203.0.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESecurity%20forces%20helped%20evacuate%20the%20Kukis%20living%20in%20predominantly%20Meitei%20areas%20and%20vice%20versa.%20They%20now%20patrol%20the%20buffer%20zone%20created%20in%20between%2C%20while%20the%20militias%20that%20have%20formed%20on%20both%20sides%20dig%20trenches%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Findia-manipur-ethnic-violence-ed5b68efb55190de3539543955f56a92%5C%22%3Ewait%20for%20an%20opportunity%20to%20attack%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%E2%80%99s%20police%20force%2C%20which%20like%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20local%20administration%20is%20made%20up%20largely%20of%20Meiteis%2C%20has%20also%20been%20segregated%2C%20with%20Kuki%20members%20either%20being%20transferred%20or%20spontaneously%20fleeing%20to%20Kuki%20areas.%20Just%20over%20two%20months%20into%20the%20crisis%2C%20the%20physical%20%E2%80%93%20and%20emotional%20%E2%80%93%20separation%20of%20the%20communities%20is%20total.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInternational%20concern%20about%20the%20Manipur%20violence%20has%20been%20muted%20so%20far%2C%20though%20on%20July%2013%20the%20European%20Parliament%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Feuropean-parliament-adopts-resolution-manipur-protection-religious-minorities%5C%22%3Epassed%20a%20resolution%3C%2Fa%3E%20asking%20the%20Indian%20government%20%E2%80%9Cto%20take%20all%20necessary%20measures%20and%20make%20the%20utmost%20effort%20to%20promptly%20halt%20the%20ongoing%20ethnic%20and%20religious%20violence%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20resolution%20also%20asked%20the%20government%20to%20end%20the%20internet%20shutdown%20and%20to%20grant%20unhindered%20access%20to%20journalists%20and%20international%20observers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSuch%20interference%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20internal%20affairs%20is%20unacceptable%2C%20and%20reflects%20a%20colonial%20mindset%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20Indian%20government%20snapped.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20the%20background%20to%20the%20crisis%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fighting%20pits%20the%20Meitei%2C%20who%20make%20up%2053%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%202.85%20million%20population%2C%20according%20to%20the%20last%20census%20in%202011%2C%20but%20occupy%20only%2010%20per%20cent%20of%20its%20land%2C%20against%20the%20Kuki%20and%2033%20other%20tribes%2C%20which%20constitute%20about%2030%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20population%20and%20are%20geographically%20more%20spread%20out%20in%20the%20poorer%20hill%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20conflict%20stems%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fmanipur-melting-pot-boiling-cauldron%5C%22%3Edecades%20of%20contestation%20over%20land%20and%20natural%20resources%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20fuelling%20deep-seated%20resentment%20among%20both%20the%20Meiteis%20and%20Kukis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManipur%20is%20one%20of%20seven%20states%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20Northeast%20region%2C%20often%20referred%20to%20as%20the%20%E2%80%9Cseven%20sisters%E2%80%9D%2C%20which%20are%20connected%20to%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20country%20by%20a%20narrow%20strip%20of%20land%20that%20skirts%20Nepal%20and%20Bangladesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20region%2C%20which%20consists%20of%20a%20mosaic%20of%C2%A0ethnicities%2C%20languages%20and%20cultures%2C%20many%20of%20them%20tribal%2C%20is%20home%20to%20some%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20oldest%20separatist%20insurgencies.%C2%A0Many%20of%20these%20erupted%20soon%20after%20independence%20in%201947%2C%20partly%20as%20a%20result%20of%20the%20administrative%20chaos%20the%20British%20colonial%20rulers%20left%20behind.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20most%20of%20the%20region%E2%80%99s%20insurgencies%20are%20dormant%2C%20limited%20to%20practicing%20extortion%20or%20stuck%20in%20various%20stages%20of%20slow-moving%20peace%20processes.%20Some%20of%20the%20remaining%20armed%20groups%20now%20operate%20largely%20from%20rear%20bases%20on%20the%20other%20side%20of%20the%20porous%20Myanmar%20border.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F01%2F04161111%2FIndian-army-personnel-walking-along-the-India-Myanmar-border-Photo-PTI.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Indian%20army%20personnel%20walking%20along%20the%20India%20Myanmar%20border.%20Credit%3A%20PTI%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-210667%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22448%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIndian%20army%20personnel%20walking%20along%20the%20India%E2%80%93Myanmar%20border.%20Photo%3A%20PTI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%2C%20as%20noted%2C%20the%20Kukis%20are%20mostly%20Christian%20and%20the%20Meitei%20mostly%20Hindu%20(small%20numbers%20of%20Meiteis%20are%20Christian%20or%20Muslim)%2C%20the%20violence%20has%20occurred%20over%20ethnic%20rather%20than%20religious%20divides.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Nagas%2C%20another%20tribal%20community%20in%20Manipur%20that%20is%20mostly%20Christian%2C%20have%20not%20been%20involved%20at%20all%2C%20while%20Kukis%20have%20attacked%20fellow%20Christians%20who%20are%20Meitei%20living%20in%20or%20near%20majority-Kuki%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20Meitei%20leaders%20have%20nonetheless%20been%20trying%20to%20portray%20the%20turmoil%20as%20religious%2C%20seemingly%20for%20reasons%20having%20to%20do%20with%20national%20politics%3A%20they%20are%20trying%20to%20rally%20support%20among%20Hindus%20elsewhere%20in%20India%2C%20including%20within%20the%20federal%20government%2C%20which%20is%20run%20by%20the%20Hindu%20nationalist%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20available%20evidence%2C%20the%20Meiteis%20appear%20to%20have%20been%20the%20more%20aggressive%20side.%20As%20Manipur%E2%80%99s%20largest%20community%2C%20they%20enjoy%20immense%20social%2C%20political%20and%20economic%20advantages%2C%20not%20least%20dominating%20the%20state%20government%2C%20and%20therefore%20its%20police%20force%2C%20which%20gives%20them%20an%20upper%20hand%20in%20the%20conflict.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E%3Cspan%20lang%3D%5C%22EN-GB%5C%22%3EWhat%20was%20the%20immediate%20trigger%20for%20the%20violence%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Kuki%3Cb%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3Ehave%20long%20been%20recognised%20as%20a%20Scheduled%20Tribe%20under%20Indian%20law%2C%20an%20affirmative%20action%20measure%20that%20assures%20tribal%20community%20members%20access%20to%20state-run%20educational%20institutions%2C%20government%20jobs%20and%20safeguards%20such%20as%20the%20exclusive%20right%20to%20buy%20and%20own%20land%20in%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20recognised%20tribal%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%C2%A0Meitei%20also%20enjoy%20certain%20benefits%20on%20account%20of%20being%20recognised%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Csocially%20and%20economically%20backward%20class%E2%80%9D%2C%20and%20a%20tiny%20segment%20of%20them%20as%20a%20Scheduled%20Caste.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%20lang%3D%5C%22EN-GB%5C%22%3EBut%20they%20have%20been%20demanding%20the%20tribal%20status%20instead%2C%20arguing%20that%20it%20is%20necessary%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%20lang%3D%5C%22EN-GB%5C%22%3Eto%20%E2%80%9Cpreserve%E2%80%9D%20the%20community%20and%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%20lang%3D%5C%22EN-IN%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fpolitical-pulse%2Fnortheast-meitei-st-demand-manipur-hc-8581664%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20lang%3D%5C%22EN-GB%5C%22%3Esave%20%5Bits%5D%20ancestral%20land%2C%20tradition%2C%20culture%20and%20language%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%20lang%3D%5C%22EN-GB%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9D.%20The%20demand%20has%20gained%20momentum%20only%20in%20the%20last%20few%20years.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Kuki%2C%20however%2C%20argue%20that%20the%20more%20numerous%20Meitei%20are%20already%20privileged.%20The%20minority%20fears%20that%20if%20the%20Meitei%20get%20Scheduled%20Tribe%20status%2C%20they%20will%20not%20only%20corner%20the%20reserved%20government%20jobs%20but%20also%20start%20acquiring%20land%20in%20the%20hills%2C%20displacing%20Kukis%20and%20other%20tribal%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20set%20off%20the%20series%20of%20protests%20culminating%20in%20clashes%20and%20sexual%20violence%20was%20a%20Manipur%20high%20court%20ruling%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20longstanding%20Meitei%20demand.%20The%20court%20made%20its%20decision%20in%20late%20March%2C%20but%20it%20became%20public%20only%20on%20April%2019%2C%20when%20the%20judgment%20appeared%20on%20the%20court%E2%80%99s%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20May%2017%20stayed%20the%20Manipur%20court%20order%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsupreme-court-manipur-hc-meitei-scheduled-tribes-list%5C%22%3Ecalling%20it%20%E2%80%9Ccompletely%20factually%20wrong%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20that%20did%20not%20calm%20tempers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20violence%20is%20also%20related%20to%20the%20civil%20war%20raging%20in%20neighbouring%20Myanmar%20since%20shortly%20after%20its%2