ns%20as%20well%20as%20others%2C%20implying%20that%20the%20Kuki%20are%20involved%20in%20the%20illegal%20drug%20trade%2C%20including%20poppy%20cultivation%2C%20in%20collaboration%20with%20transnational%20networks%20operating%20from%20Myanmar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%20lang%3D%5C%22EN-GB%5C%22%3ESome%20Kuki%20criminal%20groups%20are%20in%20fact%20running%20drugs%2C%20but%20they%20are%20just%20one%20of%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%20lang%3D%5C%22EN-IN%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fmanipur-violence-claims-counterclaims-meitei-kuki%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20lang%3D%5C%22EN-GB%5C%22%3Emany%20players%20in%20the%20illicit%20business%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%20lang%3D%5C%22EN-GB%5C%22%3E%2C%20who%20also%20include%20Meiteis%20and%20Nagas.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20allegations%20added%20to%20longstanding%C2%A0animosity%C2%A0between%C2%A0the%20two%20communities.%20The%20Meitei%20have%20long%20alleged%20that%20the%20Kuki%20are%20not%20indigenous%20to%20Manipur%20but%20were%20resettled%20in%20the%20state%20by%20the%20British%20from%20the%20nearby%20hills%20of%20Myanmar%20in%20the%20nineteenth%20century.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%20lang%3D%5C%22EN-GB%5C%22%3ETrouble%20has%20been%20brewing%20since%20August%202015%2C%20when%20a%20former%20state%20government%2C%20also%20headed%20by%20a%20Meitei%2C%20passed%20three%20laws%20that%20t%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%20lang%3D%5C%22EN-GB%5C%22%3Eribal%20communities%20perceived%20as%20designed%20to%20favour%20the%20Meitei%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%20lang%3D%5C%22EN-GB%5C%22%3E.%20The%20tribes%20saw%20these%20laws%20as%20an%20attempt%20by%20the%20Meitei%20to%20acquire%20the%20power%20to%20buy%20land%20in%20the%20hills%20and%20sow%20doubt%20about%20the%20citizenship%20of%20tribal%20groups.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20ensuing%20demonstrations%2C%20the%20security%20forces%20killed%20nine%20young%20people%20belongi