onal%20Organisation.%20Photo%3A%20Facebook%2FKuki%20National%20Organisation-KNO%20Dept.of%20Defense%2C%20January%2021%2C%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMuch%20weakened%2C%20the%20remaining%20Meitei%20and%20Kuki%20militants%20have%20diluted%20their%20initial%20demands.%20They%20engage%20mainly%20in%20extortion%2C%20rather%20than%20rebellion%2C%20and%20play%20an%20active%20role%20in%20mainstream%20politics%2C%20though%20some%20continue%20to%20seek%20various%20degrees%20of%20autonomy%20within%20India%E2%80%99s%20federal%20structure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20legacies%20of%20these%20insurgencies%2C%20however%2C%20haunt%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20political%20and%20social%20life%2C%20including%20amid%20the%20present%20unrest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20evidence%20pointing%20to%20radical%20Meitei%20outfits%20Arambai%20Tenggol%20and%20Meitei%20Leepun%20as%20the%20main%20culprits%20in%20starting%20the%20clashes%2C%20on%20May%2028%2C%20Biren%20Singh%20tried%20to%20ascribe%20responsibility%20to%20Kuki%20militants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20fight%20is%20between%20the%20state%20and%20central%20forces%20%5Band%5D%20the%20terrorists%20who%20are%20trying%20to%20break%20Manipur%E2%80%9D%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com.%2Farticle%2Findia%2Frenewed-clashes-between-militants-and-security-forces-in-manipur-8633702%2F%5C%22%3Ehe%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20telling%20the%20media%20security%20forces%20had%20killed%2040%20Kuki%20insurgents%20who%20were%20attacking%20Meitei%20civilians%20with%20sophisticated%20weapons.%C2%A0%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20not%20a%20fight%20between%20communities%E2%80%9D%2C%20he%20asserted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fchief-of-defence-staff-contradicts-manipur-cms-claim-that-violence-isnt-between-communities%5C%22%3EHe%20was%20contradicted%20two%20days%20later%20by%20the%20Indian%20army%E2%80%99s%20top%20general%2C%20Chief%20of%20Defence%20Staff%20Anil%20Chauhan%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20s