4%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fmanipur-update-indian-army-itham-modi%5C%22%3Ethe%20army%20released%20twelve%20captured%20Meitei%20militants%3C%2Fa%3E%20(all%20men)%20who%20belonged%20to%20the%20banned%20Kanglei%20Yaol%20Kangla%20Lup%20outfit%2C%20from%20whom%20they%20had%20recovered%20numerous%20arms%20and%20stores%20of%20ammunition%2C%20after%20a%20standoff%20with%20a%20mob%20of%20an%20estimated%201%2C500%20women.%20The%20women%20reportedly%20blocked%20all%20the%20roads%20in%20the%20area%20and%20refused%20to%20let%20the%20army%20carry%20on%20with%20the%20operation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%20lang%3D%5C%22EN-GB%5C%22%3EThe%20army%20said%20that%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%20lang%3D%5C%22EN-GB%5C%22%3Econsidering%20the%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%20lang%3D%5C%22EN-IN%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2F12-cadres-of-banned-manipur-extremist-group-released-after-mob-stops-army%2Farticle67006437.ece%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20lang%3D%5C%22EN-GB%5C%22%3Esensitivity%20of%20use%20of%20kinetic%20force%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%20lang%3D%5C%22EN-GB%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9D%20against%20a%20large%20crowd%20of%20women%20and%20the%20risk%20of%20casualties%2C%20the%20troops%20decided%20to%20hand%20over%20the%20militants%20and%20leave.%20The%20danger%20of%20a%20backlash%20from%20the%20Meiteis%20and%20the%20state%20government%20dominated%20by%20the%20community%20is%20the%20unspoken%20subtext.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%20lang%3D%5C%22EN-GB%5C%22%3EApart%20from%20sending%20in%20the%20central%20security%20forces%2C%20the%20federal%20government%20has%20not%20been%20particularly%20proactive%20in%20dealing%20with%20the%20Manipur%20conflict%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%20lang%3D%5C%22EN-GB%5C%22%3E%3B%20nor%20has%20it%20been%20very%20effective%20at%20dampening%20the%20unrest.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20end%20of%20M