20to%20come%20back%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%20lang%3D%5C%22EN-GB%5C%22%3EOn%20June%2010%2C%20the%20federal%20government%20took%20what%20seemed%20to%20be%20an%20ameliorative%20measure%2C%20announcing%20the%20creation%20of%20a%20committee%20made%20up%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%20lang%3D%5C%22EN-GB%5C%22%3Ethe%20chief%20minister%2C%20elected%20representatives%2C%20political%20party%20leaders%2C%20and%20Meitei%20and%20Kuki%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%20lang%3D%5C%22EN-GB%5C%22%3Erepresentatives%20to%20start%20a%20peace%20dialogue.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20initiative%20was%20an%20instant%20failure%2C%20however%2C%20as%20both%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fmanipur-kuki-biren-singh-peace-committee%5C%22%3EMeitei%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fmanipur-kuki-biren-singh-peace-committee%5C%22%3EKuki%20representatives%20refused%20to%20participate%3C%2Fa%3E%20due%20to%20disagreements%20over%20the%20committee%E2%80%99s%20composition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPrompted%20by%20indignation%20over%20the%20video%20depicting%20the%20abuse%20of%20two%20naked%20Kuki%20women%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fseventy-nine-days-after-violence-broke-out-narendra-modi-finally-talks-about-manipur%5C%22%3Espoke%20for%20the%20first%20time%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0in%20public%20about%20the%20Manipur%20violence%20on%2020%20July.%20In%20a%20brief%20statement%2C%20he%20expressed%20shock%20at%20the%20video%2C%20assuring%20the%20public%20that%20justice%20would%20be%20served%20for%20the%20survivors%20of%20sexual%20violence.%20Whether%20this%20pledge%20translates%20into%20concrete%20action%2C%20however%2C%20remains%20to%20be%20seen.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fnarendra-modi-talked-about-the-manipur-violence-but-did-he-really%5C%22%3ENarendra%20Modi%20Talked%20About%20the%20Manipur%20Violence.%20But%20Did%20He%20Really%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENational%20politics%20is%20also%20playing%20a%20part%20in%20the%C2%A0central%20state%E2%80%99s%20half-hearted%20response.%20Despite%20reports%20that%20Home%20Minister%20Shah%20is%20keeping%20a%20close%20watch%20on%20security%20conditions%20in%20the%20state%2C%20the%20absence%20of%20new%20concrete%20measures%20suggests%20that%20New%20Delhi%20has%20delegated%20the%20effort%20to%20control%20the%20violence%20to%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20Meitei-dominated%20administration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20the%20turmoil%2C%20and%20given%20that%20state%20authorities%20like%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Biren%20Singh%20are%20widely%20perceived%20as%20partisan%2C%20the%20BJP-run%20federal%20government%20could%20have%20replaced%20the%20chief%20minister%20with%20someone%20less%20polarising.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlternatively%2C%20New%20Delhi%20could%20have%20opted%20to%20impose%20president%E2%80%99s%20rule%2C%20which%20would%20allow%20the%20central%20state%20to%20assume%20command%20over%20all%20security%20forces%20in%20the%20area%20and%20recover%20stolen%20weapons%20%E2%80%93%20a%20step%20that%20would%20have%20been%20in%20keeping%20with%20the%20tough%20security%20image%20cultivated%20by%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20federal%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYet%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%202024%20national%20elections%2C%20the%20BJP%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fvideo-ramachandra-guha-karan-thapar-narendra-modi-manipur%5C%22%3Eappears%20reluctant%20to%20acknowledge%20its%20failures%20in%20Manipur%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20to%20risk%20losing%20the%20Meiteis%E2%80%99%20electoral%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E%3Cspan%20lang%3D%5C%22EN-GB%5C%22%3EWhat%20can%20be%20done%20to%20put%20an%20end%20to%20the%20violence%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20had%20kept%20mum%20on%20the%20crisis%20for%20almost%20three%20months%2C%20before%20the%20viral%20video%20forced%20him%20to%20break%20his%20silence%2C%20has%20generated%20anger%20on%20both%20sides.%20His%20statement%2C%20though%20criticised%20in%20some%20quarters%20for%20failing%20to%20address%20the%20broader%20outbreak%20of%20ethnic%20violence%20in%20Manipur%2C%20has%20encouraged%20Kuki%20women%20victims%20to%20share%20their%20testimonies%20with%20the%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20prime%20minister%20is%20popular%20in%20Manipur%20%E2%80%93%20both%20the%20Meitei%20and%20Kuki%20voted%20for%20the%20BJP%20in%20large%20numbers%20in%20two%20consecutive%20elections%20%E2%80%93%20and%20he%20could%20have%20made%20an%20immediate%20difference%20with%20an%20urgent%20personal%20appeal%20for%20peace.%20There%20is%20still%20an%20opportunity%20for%20such%20an%20intervention%2C%20though%20the%20BJP%20has%20so%20far%20appeared%20inclined%20to%20avoid%20deeper%20central%20state%20involvement%20in%20the%20crisis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F27140126%2FNarendra-Modi-in-Manipur.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22620%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F27140126%2FNarendra-Modi-in-Manipur.jpeg%20620w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F27140126%2FNarendra-Modi-in-Manipur-300x182.jpeg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-665432%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22376%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ENarendra%20Modi%20campaigning%20in%20Imphal%2C%20Manipur%E2%80%99s%20capital%20city%20in%202014.%20Photo%3A%20Twitter%2F%40PriyaaReturnz.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20given%20the%20gravity%20of%20the%20situation%2C%20the%20central%20government%20should%20put%20political%20calculations%20aside%20and%20impose%20president%E2%80%99s%20rule%20in%20Manipur.%20This%20step%20would%20place%20all%20security%20forces%20automatically%20under%20New%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20command%20and%20cause%20the%20state%20government%20to%20be%20dismissed%2C%20without%20abrogating%20citizens%E2%80%99%20basic%20rights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20past%2C%20this%20exceptional%20measure%20has%20usually%20been%20imposed%20in%20a%20conflict%E2%80%99s%20early%20stages%2C%20such%20as%20when%20deadly%20clashes%20broke%20out%20between%20the%20Nagas%20and%20Kukis%20in%201993.%20President%E2%80%99s%20rule%20has%20in%20fact%20been%20imposed%20ten%20times%20in%20the%20past%20in%20Manipur%2C%20most%20recently%20in%202001%20when%20the%20state%20government%20lost%20its%20majority%20in%20the%20local%20legislature.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20delay%2C%20there%20is%20no%20better%20solution%20at%20this%20juncture%20given%20the%20urgent%20need%20for%20a%20neutral%20administration%20in%20Manipur%20to%20guarantee%20the%20peace%20and%20mediate%20between%20the%20parties.%20President%E2%80%99s%20rule%20would%20go%20a%20long%20way%20toward%20addressing%20Kuki%20distrust%20of%20the%20state%20government%2C%20but%20unless%20handled%20deftly%20could%20antagonise%20the%20Meitei.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%20lang%3D%5C%22EN-GB%5C%22%3ETo%20placate%20the%20latter%2C%20Modi%20might%20well%20need%20to%20visit%20the%20region%20before%20imposing%20president%E2%80%99s%20rule%20for%20an%20initial%20six-month%20period%2C%20and%20make%20it%20clear%20to%20them%20(as%20well%20as%20the%20Kuki)%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%20lang%3D%5C%22EN-GB%5C%22%3Ethat%20he%20will%20protect%20their%20interests.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%20lang%3D%5C%22EN-GB%5C%22%3EMeasures%20to%20address%20the%20widespread%20sexual%20violence%20should%20be%20among%20the%20top%20priorities%20for%20the%20central%20government%20whether%20or%20not%20it%20decides%20to%20impose%20president%E2%80%99s%20rule.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%20lang%3D%5C%22EN-GB%5C%22%3E%C2%A0These%20should%20include%20sexual%20and%20reproductive%20health%20and%20psychosocial%20support%20for%20survivors%2C%20as%20well%20as%20efforts%20to%20bring%20perpetrators%20to%20justice.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProgress%20in%20these%20areas%20will%20also%20contribute%20to%20strengthening%20trust%20between%20the%20citizenry%C2%A0and%20the%20state%2C%20feeding%20into%20longer-term%20peace%20and%20reconciliation%20objectives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwomen%2Fin-manipur-violence-against-women-impunity-and-apathy-show-a-familiar-pattern-of-events%5C%22%3EIn%20Manipur%2C%20Violence%20Against%20Women%2C%20Impunity%2C%20and%20Apathy%20Show%20a%20Familiar%20Pattern%20of%20Events%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20measures%20to%20try%20to%20restore%20some%20level%20of%20comity%20between%20the%20clashing%20communities%20will%20be%20important.%20Two%20months%20after%20the%20unrest%20began%2C%20dead%20bodies%20are%20still%20lying%20unclaimed%20and%20unidentified%20in%20morgues%20because%20the%20Kuki%20are%20unable%20to%20travel%20to%20areas%20dominated%20by%20the%20Meitei%20and%20vice%20versa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20central%20security%20forces%2C%20in%20coordination%20with%20civil%20society%20organisations%20from%20both%20communities%2C%20could%20facilitate%20an%20exchange%20of%20bodies%20so%20that%20kin%20can%20proceed%20with%20proper%20funeral%20rites.%20This%20step%20could%20help%20build%20a%20modicum%20of%20confidence%20between%20the%20sides%20that%20would%2C%20ideally%2C%20allow%20for%20a%20comprehensive%20peace%20dialogue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20to%20avoid%20a%20failure%20like%20its%20first%20attempt%20in%20June%20at%20creating%20a%20peace%20committee%2C%20New%20Delhi%20should%20(when%20the%20moment%20arrives)%20consult%20widely%20among%20both%20communities%20before%20deciding%20on%20the%20composition%20of%20a%20dialogue%20panel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20much%20as%20possible%2C%20it%20should%20bring%20in%20moderates%2C%20including%20women%2C%20from%20both%20communities%2C%20preferably%20academics%20or%20civil%20society%20representatives%20who%20have%20not%20taken%20polarising%20stands%20during%20the%20violence.%20It%20should%20also%20make%20sure%20that%20members%20have%20no%20link%20to%20prominent%20politicians%20or%20militants%20on%20either%20side.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%20lang%3D%5C%22EN-GB%5C%22%3EOver%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cb%3E%3Cspan%20lang%3D%5C%22EN-GB%5C%22%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%20lang%3D%5C%22EN-GB%5C%22%3Ethe%20long%20term%2C%20the%20central%20government%20should%20consider%20putting%20talks%20with%20Kuki%20militants%20who%20signed%20the%20Suspension%20of%20Operations%20Agreement%20back%20in%202008%20on%20a%20fast%20track.%20Addressing%20Kuki%20aspirations%20for%20tribal%20autonomy%20will%20no%20doubt%20prove%20complex%2C%20as%20it%20will%20face%20stiff%20opposition%20from%20both%20the%20Meiteis%20and%20Nagas.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20it%20is%20increasingly%20clear%20that%20whether%20the%20measures%20are%20immediate%20or%20for%20the%20longer%20term%2C%20New%20Delhi%20will%20need%20to%20overcome%20its%20reticence%20and%20take%20bolder%20steps%20to%20still%20Manipur%E2%80%99s%20ethnic%20turmoil.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20has%20been%20republished%20here%20with%20permission%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.crisisgroup.org%5C%22%3Ethe%20International%20Crisis%20Group%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20where%20it%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.crisisgroup.org%2Fasia%2Fsouth-asia%2Findia%2Fethnic-clashes-roiling-manipur-pose-test-indias-modi%5C%22%3Efirst%20appeared%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690453837000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F19164339%2FUntitled-design-50.jpg%22%2C%22or