(India)%E2%80%99%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F306675%2Fanindita-chatterjee-travel-content-creator-new-mom-travelling-with-infant-pregnancy-tips%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emother%20and%20children%20trip%3C%2Fa%3E%20they%20planned%20together%20was%20to%20Puducherry%20in%20October%202021.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20planned%20the%20first%20trip%20to%20Puducherry%20as%20I%20am%20very%20familiar%20with%20the%20place.%20We%20posted%20the%20trip%20details%20on%20our%20Instagram%20page%20and%20were%20sold%20out%20in%20two%20days.%20We%20took%20six%20moms%20and%20their%20children%20with%20us%2C%20and%20everyone%20had%20a%20great%20time%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Saakshi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20response%20since%20has%20been%20immense.%20With%20over%2075%2C000%20followers%20on%20Instagram%20today%2C%20the%20duo%20have%20planned%2020%20such%20trips%20across%20five%20destinations%20%E2%80%94%20Puducherry%2C%20Coonoor%2C%20Varkala%2C%20Goa%20and%20Mysuru.%20They%20have%20also%20planned%20all-women%E2%80%99s%20trips%20to%20Lakshadweep%2C%20Andaman%20and%20Puducherry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhy%20should%20kids%20have%20all%20the%20fun%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-group%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-group__inner-container%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-gallery%20wp-block-gallery-3%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201268px)%20100vw%2C%201268px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftravel-1690375405.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221268%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22travel%20with%20kids%20india%20takes%20mothers%20and%20children%20on%20trips%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftravel-1690375405.jpg%201268w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebe