th%20disabilities%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20otherwise%20engage%20in%20regular%20childhood%20activities%20like%20going%20to%20the%20park%20and%20that%20they%20often%20had%20no%20friends.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThen%20it%20turned%20out%20that%20my%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F291203%2Fdaughter-down-syndrome-made-amarjit-singh-anand-start-chaanan-home-for-disabled-kids-punjab%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eown%20daughter%20was%20disabled%3C%2Fa%3E.%20We%20hadn%E2%80%99t%20looked%20at%20it%20that%20way%20until%20she%20had%20to%20go%20to%20school.%20Then%20her%20disabilities%20really%20became%20apparent.%20For%20us%2C%20she%20was%20just%20Moy%20Moy%2C%20this%20great%2C%20funny%2C%20little%20child.%20But%20when%20she%20started%20going%20to%20school%2C%20it%20was%20as%20if%20they%20put%20a%20spotlight%20on%20her%20difficulties.%20That%E2%80%99s%20when%20we%20realised%20this%20school%20system%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20right%20for%20Moy%20Moy.%20Everything%20at%20the%20Foundation%20has%20evolved%20from%20that.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20put%20in%20place%20many%20provisions%20in%20the%20form%20of%20laws%20and%20policies%20for%20people%20with%20disabilities%2C%20but%20the%20implementation%20remains%20questionable.%20%3Cem%3EOutlook%20India%20%3C%2Fem%3Enoted%20that%20of%20the%2078.64%20lakh%20children%20with%20disabilities%20in%20the%20country%2C%20three-fourths%20of%20those%20aged%20five%20don%E2%80%99t%20attend%20any%20educational%20institution.%20About%2012%25%20drop%20out%2C%20and%2027%25%20have%20never%20attended%20any%20educational%20institute.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20a%20UNICEF%20report%20notes%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20early%20years%20(0%20to%208%20years)%20are%20the%20most%20extraordinary%20period%20of%20growth%20and%20development%20in%20a%20child%E2%80%99s%20lifetime.%20The%20foundations%20of%20all%20learning%20are%20laid%20during%20these%20years.%20Getting%20the%20foun