%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eevils%20of%20the%20caste%20system%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20the%20film%20also%20served%20as%20the%20launchpad%20for%20Chhollywood%20(as%20the%20film%20industry%20of%20Chhattisgarh%20is%20popularly%20known)%20and%20was%20screened%20in%20Raipur%20in%202015%20at%20a%20film%20festival%20to%20mark%20the%20jubilee%20of%20this%20event.%20For%20Nayak%2C%20this%20event%20held%20tremendous%20significance.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20196px)%20100vw%2C%20196px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FManu-4-1689943596.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22196%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22While%20members%20of%20the%20Brahmin%20community%20in%20Raipur%20threatened%20to%20ban%20the%20film%2C%20it%20was%20applauded%20by%20many%20important%20figures%2C%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FManu-4-1689943596.jpg%20196w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FManu-4-1689943596-127x300.jpg%20127w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FManu-4-1689943596-150x354.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-324750%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22462%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EWhile%20members%20of%20the%20Brahmin%20community%20in%20Raipur%20threatened%20to%20ban%20the%20film%2C%20it%20was%20applauded%20by%20many%20important%20figures%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20A%20photobook%20by%20Aayush%20Chandrawanshi%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBehind%20the%20scenes%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20%3Cem%3EKahi%20Debe%20Sandesh%20%3C%2Fem%3Eblew%20up%20the%20film%20industry%20with%20conversation%20about%20films%20centric%20on%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebett